114 OCP_BOOL IsoT_IMPEC::UpdateProperty(Reservoir& rs, OCPControl& ctrl)
115 {
116  OCP_DBL& dt = ctrl.current_dt;
117 
118  // First check : Pressure check
119  if (!ctrl.Check(rs, { "BulkP", "WellP" })) {
120  return OCP_FALSE;
121  }
122 
123  // Calculate Flux between bulks and between bulks and wells
124  CalFlux(rs);
125 
126  // Second check : CFL check
127  rs.CalCFL(dt);
128  if (!ctrl.Check(rs, { "CFL" })) {
129  ResetToLastTimeStep01(rs, ctrl);
130  cout << "CFL is too big" << endl;
131  return OCP_FALSE;
132  }
133 
134  MassConserve(rs, dt);
135 
136  // Third check: Ni check
137  if (!ctrl.Check(rs, { "BulkNi" })) {
138  ResetToLastTimeStep02(rs, ctrl);
139  return OCP_FALSE;
140  }
141 
142  CalRock(rs.bulk);
143  CalFlash(rs.bulk);
144 
145  // Fouth check: Volume error check
146  if (!ctrl.Check(rs, { "BulkVe" })) {
147  ResetToLastTimeStep03(rs, ctrl);
148  return OCP_FALSE;
149  }
150 
151  CalKrPc(rs.bulk);
152  CalBulkFlux(rs);
153 
154  return OCP_TRUE;
155 }

285 void IsoT_IMPEC::PassFlashValue(Bulk& bk, const OCP_USI& n) const
286 {
287  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
288  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
289  const OCP_USI bIdp = n * np;
290  const USI pvtnum = bk.PVTNUM[n];
291 
292  bk.phaseNum[n] = 0;
293  bk.Nt[n] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetNt();
294  bk.vf[n] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetVf();
295 
296  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
297  // Important! Saturation must be passed no matter if the phase exists. This is
298  // because it will be used to calculate relative permeability and capillary
299  // pressure at each time step. Make sure that all saturations are updated at
300  // each step!
301  bk.phaseExist[bIdp + j] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetPhaseExist(j);
302  bk.S[bIdp + j] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetS(j);
303  if (bk.phaseExist[bIdp + j]) {
304  bk.phaseNum[n]++;
305  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
306  bk.xij[bIdp * nc + j * nc + i] =
307  bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetXij(j, i);
308  }
309  bk.vj[bIdp + j] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetVj(j);
310  bk.rho[bIdp + j] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetRho(j);
311  bk.xi[bIdp + j] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetXi(j);
312  bk.mu[bIdp + j] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetMu(j);
313  }
314  }
315 
316  bk.vfP[n] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetVfP();
317  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
318  bk.vfi[n * nc + i] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetVfi(i);
319  }
320 }

341 void IsoT_IMPEC::CalBulkFlux(Reservoir& rs) const
342 {
343  const Bulk& bk = rs.bulk;
344  BulkConn& conn = rs.conn;
345  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
346 
347  // calculate a step flux using iteratorConn
348  OCP_USI bId, eId, uId;
349  OCP_USI bId_np_j, eId_np_j;
350  OCP_BOOL exbegin, exend, exup;
351  OCP_DBL rho, dP, Akd;
352 
353 
354  for (OCP_USI c = 0; c < conn.numConn; c++) {
355  bId = conn.iteratorConn[c].BId();
356  eId = conn.iteratorConn[c].EId();
357  Akd = CONV1 * CONV2 * conn.iteratorConn[c].Area();
358 
359  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
360  bId_np_j = bId * np + j;
361  eId_np_j = eId * np + j;
362 
363  exbegin = bk.phaseExist[bId_np_j];
364  exend = bk.phaseExist[eId_np_j];
365 
366  if ((exbegin) && (exend)) {
367  rho = (bk.rho[bId_np_j] + bk.rho[eId_np_j]) / 2;
368  }
369  else if (exbegin && (!exend)) {
370  rho = bk.rho[bId_np_j];
371  }
372  else if ((!exbegin) && (exend)) {
373  rho = bk.rho[eId_np_j];
374  }
375  else {
376  conn.upblock[c * np + j] = bId;
377  continue;
378  }
379 
380  dP = (bk.Pj[bId_np_j] - GRAVITY_FACTOR * rho * bk.depth[bId])
381  - (bk.Pj[eId_np_j] - GRAVITY_FACTOR * rho * bk.depth[eId]);
382  if (dP < 0) {
383  uId = eId;
384  exup = exend;
385  }
386  else {
387  uId = bId;
388  exup = exbegin;
389  }
390 
391  conn.upblock_Rho[c * np + j] = rho;
392  conn.upblock[c * np + j] = uId;
393 
394  if (exup) {
395  conn.upblock_Trans[c * np + j] = Akd * bk.kr[uId * np + j] / bk.mu[uId * np + j];
396  conn.upblock_Velocity[c * np + j] = conn.upblock_Trans[c * np + j] * dP;
397  }
398  else {
399  conn.upblock_Trans[c * np + j] = 0;
400  conn.upblock_Velocity[c * np + j] = 0;
401  }
402  }
403  }
404 }

407 void IsoT_IMPEC::MassConserve(Reservoir& rs, const OCP_DBL& dt) const
408 {
409 
410  // Bulk to Bulk
411  Bulk& bk = rs.bulk;
412  const BulkConn& conn = rs.conn;
413 
414  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
415  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
416 
417  OCP_USI bId, eId, uId;
418  OCP_USI uId_np_j;
419  OCP_DBL phaseVelocity, dNi;
420 
421  for (OCP_USI c = 0; c < conn.numConn; c++) {
422  bId = conn.iteratorConn[c].BId();
423  eId = conn.iteratorConn[c].EId();
424 
425  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
426  uId = conn.upblock[c * np + j];
427  uId_np_j = uId * np + j;
428 
429  if (!bk.phaseExist[uId_np_j]) continue;
430 
431  phaseVelocity = conn.upblock_Velocity[c * np + j];
432  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
433  dNi = dt * phaseVelocity * bk.xi[uId_np_j] *
434  bk.xij[uId_np_j * nc + i];
435  bk.Ni[eId * nc + i] += dNi;
436  bk.Ni[bId * nc + i] -= dNi;
437  }
438  }
439  }
440 
441  // Well to Bulk
442  for (auto& wl : rs.allWells.wells) {
443  if (wl.IsOpen()) {
444  for (USI p = 0; p < wl.PerfNum(); p++) {
445  OCP_USI k = wl.PerfLocation(p);
446  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
447  bk.Ni[k * nc + i] -= wl.PerfQi_lbmol(p, i) * dt;
448  }
449  }
450  }
451  }
452 
453 }

456 void IsoT_IMPEC::AssembleMatBulks(LinearSystem& ls, const Reservoir& rs, const OCP_DBL& dt) const
457 {
458 
459  const Bulk& bk = rs.bulk;
460  const BulkConn& conn = rs.conn;
461  const OCP_USI nb = bk.numBulk;
462  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
463  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
464 
465  ls.AddDim(nb);
466 
467  // accumulate term
468  OCP_DBL Vpp, Vp, vf, vfP, P;
469  for (OCP_USI n = 0; n < nb; n++) {
470  vf = bk.vf[n];
471  vfP = bk.vfP[n];
472  P = bk.lP[n];
473  Vpp = bk.v[n] * bk.poroP[n];
474  Vp = bk.rockVp[n];
475 
476  ls.NewDiag(n, Vpp - vfP);
477  ls.AddRhs(n, (Vpp - vfP) * P + dt * (vf - Vp));
478  }
479 
480  // flux term
481  OCP_USI bId, eId, uId_np_j;
482  OCP_DBL valupi, valdowni, valup, rhsup, valdown, rhsdown;
483  OCP_DBL dD, tmp;
484 
485  // Be careful when first bulk has no neighbors!
486  for (OCP_USI c = 0; c < conn.numConn; c++) {
487  bId = conn.iteratorConn[c].BId();
488  eId = conn.iteratorConn[c].EId();
489  dD = GRAVITY_FACTOR * (bk.depth[bId] - bk.depth[eId]);
490 
491  valup = 0;
492  rhsup = 0;
493  valdown = 0;
494  rhsdown = 0;
495 
496  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
497  uId_np_j = conn.upblock[c * np + j] * np + j;
498  if (!bk.phaseExist[uId_np_j]) continue;
499 
500  valupi = 0;
501  valdowni = 0;
502 
503  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
504  valupi += bk.vfi[bId * nc + i] * bk.xij[uId_np_j * nc + i];
505  valdowni += bk.vfi[eId * nc + i] * bk.xij[uId_np_j * nc + i];
506  }
507 
508  tmp = bk.xi[uId_np_j] * conn.upblock_Trans[c * np + j] * dt;
509  valup += tmp * valupi;
510  valdown += tmp * valdowni;
511  tmp *= conn.upblock_Rho[c * np + j] * dD -
512  (bk.Pc[bId * np + j] - bk.Pc[eId * np + j]);
513  rhsup += tmp * valupi;
514  rhsdown -= tmp * valdowni;
515  }
516  ls.AddDiag(bId, valup);
517  ls.AddDiag(eId, valdown);
518  ls.NewOffDiag(bId, eId, -valup);
519  ls.NewOffDiag(eId, bId, -valdown);
520  ls.AddRhs(bId, rhsup);
521  ls.AddRhs(eId, rhsdown);
522  }
523 }

557 void IsoT_IMPEC::AssembleMatInjWells(LinearSystem& ls, const Bulk& bk, const Well& wl, const OCP_DBL& dt) const
558 {
559  const OCP_USI wId = ls.AddDim(1) - 1;
560  ls.NewDiag(wId, 0.0);
561 
562  OCP_DBL Vfi_zi, valb, valw, bb, bw;
563 
564  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
565 
566  for (USI p = 0; p < wl.PerfNum(); p++) {
567  const OCP_USI n = wl.PerfLocation(p);
568 
569  Vfi_zi = 0;
570  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
571  Vfi_zi += bk.vfi[n * nc + i] * wl.InjZi(i);
572  }
573 
574  valw = dt * wl.PerfXi(p) * wl.PerfTransInj(p);
575  bw = valw * wl.DG(p);
576  valb = valw * Vfi_zi;
577  bb = valb * wl.DG(p);
578 
579  // Bulk to Well
580  ls.AddDiag(n, valb);
581  ls.NewOffDiag(n, wId, -valb);
582  ls.AddRhs(n, bb);
583 
584  // Well to Bulk
585  switch (wl.OptMode()) {
586  case RATE_MODE:
587  case ORATE_MODE:
588  case GRATE_MODE:
589  case WRATE_MODE:
590  case LRATE_MODE:
591  ls.AddDiag(wId, valw);
592  ls.NewOffDiag(wId, n, -valw);
593  ls.AddRhs(wId, -bw);
594  break;
595  case BHP_MODE:
596  ls.NewOffDiag(wId, n, 0);
597  break;
598  default:
599  OCP_ABORT("Wrong well option mode!");
600  }
601  }
602 
603  // Well Self
604  switch (wl.OptMode()) {
605  case RATE_MODE:
606  case ORATE_MODE:
607  case GRATE_MODE:
608  case WRATE_MODE:
609  case LRATE_MODE:
610  ls.AddRhs(wId, dt * wl.MaxRate());
611  break;
612  case BHP_MODE:
613  ls.AddDiag(wId, dt);
614  ls.AddRhs(wId, dt * wl.MaxBHP());
615  ls.AssignGuess(wId, wl.MaxBHP());
616  break;
617  default:
618  OCP_ABORT("Wrong well option mode!");
619  }
620 }

622 void IsoT_IMPEC::AssembleMatProdWells(LinearSystem& ls, const Bulk& bk, const Well& wl, const OCP_DBL& dt) const
623 {
624 
625  const OCP_USI wId = ls.AddDim(1) - 1;
626  ls.NewDiag(wId, 0.0);
627 
628  // Set Prod Weight
629  if (wl.OptMode() != BHP_MODE) wl.CalProdWeight(bk);
630 
631  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
632  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
633 
634  for (USI p = 0; p < wl.PerfNum(); p++) {
635  const OCP_USI n = wl.PerfLocation(p);
636 
637  OCP_DBL valb = 0;
638  OCP_DBL bb = 0;
639  OCP_DBL valw = 0;
640  OCP_DBL bw = 0;
641 
642  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
643  if (!bk.phaseExist[n * np + j]) continue;
644 
645  OCP_DBL tempb = 0;
646  OCP_DBL tempw = 0;
647 
648  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
649  tempb += bk.vfi[n * nc + i] *
650  bk.xij[n * np * nc + j * nc + i];
651  tempw +=
652  wl.ProdWeight(i) * bk.xij[n * np * nc + j * nc + i];
653  }
654  OCP_DBL trans = dt * wl.PerfTransj(p,j) * bk.xi[n * np + j];
655  valb += tempb * trans;
656  valw += tempw * trans;
657 
658  OCP_DBL dP = wl.DG(p) - bk.Pc[n * np + j];
659  bb += tempb * trans * dP;
660  bw += tempw * trans * dP;
661  }
662 
663  // Bulk to Well
664  ls.AddDiag(n, valb);
665  ls.NewOffDiag(n, wId, -valb);
666  ls.AddRhs(n, bb);
667 
668  // Well to Bulk
669  switch (wl.OptMode()) {
670  case RATE_MODE:
671  case ORATE_MODE:
672  case GRATE_MODE:
673  case WRATE_MODE:
674  case LRATE_MODE:
675  ls.AddDiag(wId, -valw);
676  ls.NewOffDiag(wId, n, valw);
677  ls.AddRhs(wId, bw);
678  break;
679  case BHP_MODE:
680  ls.NewOffDiag(wId, n, 0.0);
681  break;
682  default:
683  OCP_ABORT("Wrong well option mode!");
684  }
685  }
686 
687  // Well Self
688  switch (wl.OptMode()) {
689  case RATE_MODE:
690  case ORATE_MODE:
691  case GRATE_MODE:
692  case WRATE_MODE:
693  case LRATE_MODE:
694  ls.AddRhs(wId, dt * wl.MaxRate());
695  break;
696  case BHP_MODE:
697  ls.AddDiag(wId, dt);
698  ls.AddRhs(wId, dt * wl.MinBHP());
699  ls.AssignGuess(wId, wl.MinBHP());
700  break;
701  default:
702  OCP_ABORT("Wrong well option mode!");
703  }
704 }

707 void IsoT_IMPEC::GetSolution(Reservoir& rs, const vector<OCP_DBL>& u)
708 {
709  Bulk& bk = rs.bulk;
710  const OCP_USI nb = bk.numBulk;
711  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
712 
713  // Bulk
714  for (OCP_USI n = 0; n < nb; n++) {
715  bk.P[n] = u[n];
716  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
717  bk.Pj[n * np + j] = bk.P[n] + bk.Pc[n * np + j];
718  }
719  }
720 
721  // Well
722  USI wId = nb;
723  for (auto& wl : rs.allWells.wells) {
724  if (wl.IsOpen()) {
725  wl.SetBHP(u[wId]);
726  wl.CalPerfP();
727  wId++;
728  }
729  }

900 void IsoT_FIM::SolveLinearSystem(LinearSystem& ls,
901  Reservoir& rs,
902  OCPControl& ctrl) const
903 {
904 #ifdef DEBUG
905  // Check if inf or nan occurs in A and b
906  ls.CheckEquation();
907 #endif // DEBUG
908 
909  // Assemble external linear solver with internal A and b
910  ls.AssembleMatLinearSolver();
911  // Solve linear system
912  GetWallTime Timer;
913  Timer.Start();
914  int status = ls.Solve();
915  if (status < 0) {
916  status = ls.GetNumIters();
917  }
918  // Record time, iterations
919  ctrl.RecordTimeLS(Timer.Stop() / 1000);
920  ctrl.UpdateIterLS(status);
921  ctrl.UpdateIterNR();
922 
923 #ifdef DEBUG
924  // Output A, b, x
925  //ls.OutputLinearSystem("testA_FIM.out", "testb_FIM.out");
926  //ls.OutputSolution("testx_FIM.out");
927  // Check if inf or nan occurs in solution
928  ls.CheckSolution();
929 #endif // DEBUG
930 
931  // Get solution from linear system to Reservoir
932  GetSolution(rs, ls.GetSolution(), ctrl);
933  // rs.PrintSolFIM(ctrl.workDir + "testPNi.out");
934  ls.ClearData();
935 }

963 OCP_BOOL IsoT_FIM::FinishNR(Reservoir& rs, OCPControl& ctrl)
964 {
965  OCP_USI dSn;
966 
967  const OCP_DBL NRdSmax = rs.GetNRdSmax(dSn);
968  const OCP_DBL NRdPmax = rs.GetNRdPmax();
969  // const OCP_DBL NRdNmax = rs.GetNRdNmax();
970 
971  if (((rs.bulk.res.maxRelRes_V <= rs.bulk.res.maxRelRes0_V * ctrl.ctrlNR.NRtol ||
972  rs.bulk.res.maxRelRes_V <= ctrl.ctrlNR.NRtol ||
973  rs.bulk.res.maxRelRes_N <= ctrl.ctrlNR.NRtol) &&
974  rs.bulk.res.maxWellRelRes_mol <= ctrl.ctrlNR.NRtol) ||
975  (fabs(NRdPmax) <= ctrl.ctrlNR.NRdPmin &&
976  fabs(NRdSmax) <= ctrl.ctrlNR.NRdSmin)) {
977 
978  if (!ctrl.Check(rs, { "WellP" })) {
979  ResetToLastTimeStep(rs, ctrl);
980  return OCP_FALSE;
981  }
982  else {
983  return OCP_TRUE;
984  }
985  }
986  else if (ctrl.iterNR >= ctrl.ctrlNR.maxNRiter) {
987  ctrl.current_dt *= ctrl.ctrlTime.cutFacNR;
988  ResetToLastTimeStep(rs, ctrl);
989  cout << "### WARNING: NR not fully converged! Cut time step size and repeat! "
990  "current dt = "
991  << fixed << setprecision(3) << ctrl.current_dt << " days\n";
992  return OCP_FALSE;
993  }
994  else {
995  return OCP_FALSE;
996  }
997 }

1124 {

1128  for (USI i = 0; i < bk.numCom; i++) {

1143  &bk.xij[n * bk.numPhase * bk.numCom], n);

1148 
1149 void IsoT_FIM::PassFlashValue(Bulk& bk, const OCP_USI& n) const
1150 {
1151  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
1152  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
1153  const OCP_USI bIdp = n * np;
1154  const USI pvtnum = bk.PVTNUM[n];
1155  USI len = 0;
1156 
1157  bk.phaseNum[n] = 0;
1158  bk.Nt[n] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetNt();
1159  bk.vf[n] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetVf();
1160 
1161  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
1162  // Important! Saturation must be passed no matter if the phase exists. This is
1163  // because it will be used to calculate relative permeability and capillary
1164  // pressure at each time step. Make sure that all saturations are updated at
1165  // each step!
1166  bk.S[bIdp + j] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetS(j);
1167  bk.dSNR[bIdp + j] = bk.S[bIdp + j] - bk.dSNR[bIdp + j];
1168  if (bk.phaseExist[bIdp + j]) {
1169  if (fabs(bk.maxNRdSSP) < fabs(bk.dSNR[bIdp + j] - bk.dSNRP[bIdp + j])) {
1170  bk.maxNRdSSP = bk.dSNR[bIdp + j] - bk.dSNRP[bIdp + j];
1171  bk.index_maxNRdSSP = n;
1172  }
1173  }
1174 
1175  bk.phaseExist[bIdp + j] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetPhaseExist(j);
1176  if (bk.phaseExist[bIdp + j]) {
1177  bk.phaseNum[n]++;
1178  bk.rho[bIdp + j] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetRho(j);
1179  bk.xi[bIdp + j] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetXi(j);
1180  bk.mu[bIdp + j] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetMu(j);
1181 
1182  // Derivatives
1183  bk.rhoP[bIdp + j] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetRhoP(j);
1184  bk.xiP[bIdp + j] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetXiP(j);
1185  bk.muP[bIdp + j] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetMuP(j);
1186 
1187  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
1188  bk.xij[bIdp * nc + j * nc + i] =
1189  bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetXij(j, i);
1190  bk.rhox[bIdp * nc + j * nc + i] =
1191  bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetRhoX(j, i);
1192  bk.xix[bIdp * nc + j * nc + i] =
1193  bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetXiX(j, i);
1194  bk.mux[bIdp * nc + j * nc + i] =
1195  bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetMuX(j, i);
1196  }
1197  }
1198 
1199  bk.pSderExist[bIdp + j] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetPSderExist(j);
1200  bk.pVnumCom[bIdp + j] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetPVnumCom(j);
1201  if (bk.pSderExist[bIdp + j]) len++;
1202  len += bk.pVnumCom[bIdp + j];
1203  }
1204 
1205  bk.vfP[n] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetVfP();
1206  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
1207  bk.vfi[n * nc + i] = bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetVfi(i);
1208  }
1209 
1210 #ifdef OCP_OLD_FIM
1211  Dcopy(bk.maxLendSdP, &bk.dSec_dPri[n * bk.maxLendSdP], &bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetDXsDXp()[0]);
1212 #else
1213  bk.bRowSizedSdP[n] = len;
1214  len *= (nc + 1);
1215  Dcopy(len, &bk.dSec_dPri[n * bk.maxLendSdP], &bk.flashCal[pvtnum]->GetDXsDXp()[0]);
1216 #endif // OCP_OLD_FIM

1233 void IsoT_FIM::CalRes(Reservoir& rs, const OCP_DBL& dt, const OCP_BOOL& resetRes0) const
1234 {
1235  const Bulk& bk = rs.bulk;
1236  const USI nb = bk.numBulk;
1237  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
1238  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
1239  const USI len = nc + 1;
1240  OCPRes& Res = bk.res;
1241  BulkConn& conn = rs.conn;
1242 
1243  Res.SetZero();
1244 
1245  // Bulk to Bulk
1246 
1247  OCP_USI bId, eId, uId, bIdb;
1248  // Accumalation Term
1249  for (OCP_USI n = 0; n < nb; n++) {
1250  bId = n * len;
1251  bIdb = n * nc;
1252  Res.resAbs[bId] = bk.rockVp[n] - bk.vf[n];
1253  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
1254  Res.resAbs[bId + 1 + i] = bk.Ni[bIdb + i] - bk.lNi[bIdb + i];
1255  }
1256  }
1257 
1258  OCP_USI bId_np_j, eId_np_j, uId_np_j;
1259  OCP_DBL rho, dP, dNi, Akd;
1260 
1261  // Flux Term
1262  // Calculate the upblock at the same time.
1263  for (OCP_USI c = 0; c < conn.numConn; c++) {
1264  bId = conn.iteratorConn[c].BId();
1265  eId = conn.iteratorConn[c].EId();
1266  Akd = CONV1 * CONV2 * conn.iteratorConn[c].Area();
1267 
1268  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
1269  bId_np_j = bId * np + j;
1270  eId_np_j = eId * np + j;
1271 
1272  OCP_BOOL exbegin = bk.phaseExist[bId_np_j];
1273  OCP_BOOL exend = bk.phaseExist[eId_np_j];
1274 
1275  if ((exbegin) && (exend)) {
1276  rho = (bk.rho[bId_np_j] + bk.rho[eId_np_j]) / 2;
1277  }
1278  else if (exbegin && (!exend)) {
1279  rho = bk.rho[bId_np_j];
1280  }
1281  else if ((!exbegin) && (exend)) {
1282  rho = bk.rho[eId_np_j];
1283  }
1284  else {
1285  conn.upblock[c * np + j] = bId;
1286  conn.upblock_Rho[c * np + j] = 0;
1287  continue;
1288  }
1289 
1290  uId = bId;
1291  dP = (bk.Pj[bId_np_j] - GRAVITY_FACTOR * rho * bk.depth[bId]) -
1292  (bk.Pj[eId_np_j] - GRAVITY_FACTOR * rho * bk.depth[eId]);
1293  if (dP < 0) {
1294  uId = eId;
1295  }
1296  conn.upblock_Rho[c * np + j] = rho;
1297  conn.upblock[c * np + j] = uId;
1298  uId_np_j = uId * np + j;
1299 
1300  if (bk.phaseExist[uId_np_j]) {
1301  conn.upblock_Velocity[c * np + j] =
1302  Akd * bk.kr[uId_np_j] / bk.mu[uId_np_j] * dP;
1303  }
1304  else {
1305  conn.upblock_Velocity[c * np + j] = 0;
1306  continue;
1307  }
1308 
1309  OCP_DBL tmp = dt * Akd * bk.xi[uId_np_j] * bk.kr[uId_np_j] /
1310  bk.mu[uId_np_j] * dP;
1311 
1312  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
1313  dNi = tmp * bk.xij[uId_np_j * nc + i];
1314  Res.resAbs[bId * len + 1 + i] += dNi;
1315  Res.resAbs[eId * len + 1 + i] -= dNi;
1316  }
1317  }
1318  }
1319 
1320  // Well to Bulk
1321  USI wId = nb * len;
1322  for (const auto& wl : rs.allWells.wells) {
1323  if (wl.IsOpen()) {
1324  // Well to Bulk
1325  for (USI p = 0; p < wl.PerfNum(); p++) {
1326  const OCP_USI k = wl.PerfLocation(p);
1327  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
1328  Res.resAbs[k * len + 1 + i] += wl.PerfQi_lbmol(p, i) * dt;
1329  }
1330  }
1331  // Well Self
1332  if (wl.WellType() == INJ) {
1333  // Injection
1334  switch (wl.OptMode()) {
1335  case BHP_MODE:
1336  // bhp = opt.maxBHP;
1337  // Res.resAbs[bId] = bhp - opt.maxBHP;
1338  Res.resAbs[wId] = wl.BHP() - wl.MaxBHP();
1339  break;
1340  case RATE_MODE:
1341  case ORATE_MODE:
1342  case GRATE_MODE:
1343  case WRATE_MODE:
1344  case LRATE_MODE:
1345  Res.resAbs[wId] = wl.MaxRate();
1346  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
1347  Res.resAbs[wId] += wl.Qi_lbmol(i);
1348  }
1349  //if (opt.reInj) {
1350  // for (auto& w : opt.connWell) {
1351  // OCP_DBL tmp = 0;
1352  // for (USI i = 0; i < numCom; i++) {
1353  // tmp += allWell[w].qi_lbmol[i];
1354  // }
1355  // tmp *= opt.reInjFactor;
1356  // Res.resAbs[bId] += tmp;
1357  // }
1358  //}
1359  Res.maxWellRelRes_mol =
1360  max(Res.maxWellRelRes_mol, fabs(Res.resAbs[wId] / wl.MaxRate()));
1361  break;
1362  default:
1363  OCP_ABORT("Wrong well opt mode!");
1364  break;
1365  }
1366  }
1367  else {
1368  // Production
1369  switch (wl.OptMode()) {
1370  case BHP_MODE:
1371  //bhp = opt.minBHP;
1372  //Res.resAbs[bId] = bhp - opt.minBHP;
1373  Res.resAbs[wId] = wl.BHP() - wl.MinBHP();
1374  break;
1375  case RATE_MODE:
1376  case ORATE_MODE:
1377  case GRATE_MODE:
1378  case WRATE_MODE:
1379  case LRATE_MODE:
1380  wl.CalProdWeight(bk);
1381  Res.resAbs[wId] = -wl.MaxRate();
1382  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
1383  Res.resAbs[wId] += wl.Qi_lbmol(i) * wl.ProdWeight(i);
1384  }
1385  Res.maxWellRelRes_mol =
1386  max(Res.maxWellRelRes_mol, fabs(Res.resAbs[wId] / wl.MaxRate()));
1387  break;
1388  default:
1389  OCP_ABORT("Wrong well opt mode!");
1390  break;
1391  }
1392  }
1393  wId += len;
1394  }
1395  }
1396 
1397 
1398  // Calculate RelRes
1399  OCP_DBL tmp;
1400  for (OCP_USI n = 0; n < nb; n++) {
1401 
1402  for (USI i = 0; i < len; i++) {
1403  tmp = fabs(Res.resAbs[n * len + i] / bk.rockVp[n]);
1404  if (Res.maxRelRes_V < tmp) {
1405  Res.maxRelRes_V = tmp;
1406  Res.maxId_V = n;
1407  }
1408  Res.resRelV[n] += tmp * tmp;
1409  }
1410  Res.resRelV[n] = sqrt(Res.resRelV[n]);
1411 
1412  for (USI i = 1; i < len; i++) {
1413  tmp = fabs(Res.resAbs[n * len + i] / bk.Nt[n]);
1414  if (Res.maxRelRes_N < tmp) {
1415  Res.maxRelRes_N = tmp;
1416  Res.maxId_N = n;
1417  }
1418  Res.resRelN[n] += tmp * tmp;
1419  }
1420  Res.resRelN[n] = sqrt(Res.resRelN[n]);
1421  }
1422 
1423  Dscalar(Res.resAbs.size(), -1.0, Res.resAbs.data());
1424  if (resetRes0) Res.SetInitRes();
1425 }

1427 
1428 void IsoT_FIM::AssembleMatBulks(LinearSystem& ls,
1429  const Reservoir& rs,
1430  const OCP_DBL& dt) const
1431 {
1432  const Bulk& bk = rs.bulk;
1433  const BulkConn& conn = rs.conn;
1434  const OCP_USI nb = bk.numBulk;
1435  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
1436  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
1437  const USI ncol = nc + 1;
1438  const USI ncol2 = np * nc + np;
1439  const USI bsize = ncol * ncol;
1440  const USI bsize2 = ncol * ncol2;
1441 
1442  ls.AddDim(nb);
1443 
1444  vector<OCP_DBL> bmat(bsize, 0);
1445  // Accumulation term
1446  for (USI i = 1; i < ncol; i++) {
1447  bmat[i * ncol + i] = 1;
1448  }
1449  for (OCP_USI n = 0; n < nb; n++) {
1450  bmat[0] = bk.v[n] * bk.poroP[n] - bk.vfP[n];
1451  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
1452  bmat[i + 1] = -bk.vfi[n * nc + i];
1453  }
1454  ls.NewDiag(n, bmat);
1455  }
1456 
1457  // flux term
1458  OCP_DBL Akd;
1459  OCP_DBL transJ, transIJ;
1460  vector<OCP_DBL> dFdXpB(bsize, 0); // begin bulk: dF / dXp
1461  vector<OCP_DBL> dFdXpE(bsize, 0); // end bulk: dF / dXp
1462  vector<OCP_DBL> dFdXsB(bsize2, 0); // begin bulk: dF / dXs
1463  vector<OCP_DBL> dFdXsE(bsize2, 0); // end bulk: dF / dXs
1464  OCP_DBL* dFdXpU; // up bulk: dF / dXp
1465  OCP_DBL* dFdXpD; // down bulk: dF / dXp
1466  OCP_DBL* dFdXsU; // up bulk: dF / dXs
1467  OCP_DBL* dFdXsD; // down bulk: dF / dXs
1468 
1469  OCP_USI bId, eId, uId;
1470  OCP_USI bId_np_j, eId_np_j, uId_np_j, dId_np_j;
1471  OCP_BOOL phaseExistBj, phaseExistEj, phaseExistDj;
1472  OCP_DBL kr, mu, xi, xij, xiP, muP, rhox, xix, mux;
1473  OCP_DBL dP, dGamma;
1474  OCP_DBL rhoWghtU, rhoWghtD;
1475  OCP_DBL tmp;
1476 
1477  for (OCP_USI c = 0; c < conn.numConn; c++) {
1478 
1479  fill(dFdXpB.begin(), dFdXpB.end(), 0.0);
1480  fill(dFdXpE.begin(), dFdXpE.end(), 0.0);
1481  fill(dFdXsB.begin(), dFdXsB.end(), 0.0);
1482  fill(dFdXsE.begin(), dFdXsE.end(), 0.0);
1483 
1484  bId = conn.iteratorConn[c].BId();
1485  eId = conn.iteratorConn[c].EId();
1486  Akd = CONV1 * CONV2 * conn.iteratorConn[c].Area();
1487  dGamma = GRAVITY_FACTOR * (bk.depth[bId] - bk.depth[eId]);
1488 
1489  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
1490  uId = conn.upblock[c * np + j];
1491  uId_np_j = uId * np + j;
1492  if (!bk.phaseExist[uId_np_j]) continue;
1493  bId_np_j = bId * np + j;
1494  eId_np_j = eId * np + j;
1495  phaseExistBj = bk.phaseExist[bId_np_j];
1496  phaseExistEj = bk.phaseExist[eId_np_j];
1497 
1498  if (bId == uId) {
1499  dFdXpU = &dFdXpB[0];
1500  dFdXpD = &dFdXpE[0];
1501  dFdXsU = &dFdXsB[0];
1502  dFdXsD = &dFdXsE[0];
1503  phaseExistDj = phaseExistEj;
1504  dId_np_j = eId_np_j;
1505  }
1506  else {
1507  dFdXpU = &dFdXpE[0];
1508  dFdXpD = &dFdXpB[0];
1509  dFdXsU = &dFdXsE[0];
1510  dFdXsD = &dFdXsB[0];
1511  phaseExistDj = phaseExistBj;
1512  dId_np_j = bId_np_j;
1513  }
1514  if (phaseExistDj) {
1515  rhoWghtU = 0.5;
1516  rhoWghtD = 0.5;
1517  }
1518  else {
1519  rhoWghtU = 1;
1520  rhoWghtD = 0;
1521  }
1522 
1523  dP = bk.Pj[bId_np_j] - bk.Pj[eId_np_j] -
1524  conn.upblock_Rho[c * np + j] * dGamma;
1525  xi = bk.xi[uId_np_j];
1526  kr = bk.kr[uId_np_j];
1527  mu = bk.mu[uId_np_j];
1528  muP = bk.muP[uId_np_j];
1529  xiP = bk.xiP[uId_np_j];
1530  transJ = Akd * kr / mu;
1531 
1532  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
1533  xij = bk.xij[uId_np_j * nc + i];
1534  transIJ = xij * xi * transJ;
1535 
1536  // dP
1537  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] += transIJ;
1538  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] -= transIJ;
1539 
1540  tmp = transJ * xiP * xij * dP;
1541  tmp += -transIJ * muP / mu * dP;
1542  dFdXpU[(i + 1) * ncol] += (tmp - transIJ * rhoWghtU * bk.rhoP[uId_np_j] * dGamma);
1543  dFdXpD[(i + 1) * ncol] += -transIJ * rhoWghtD * bk.rhoP[dId_np_j] * dGamma;
1544 
1545  // dS
1546  for (USI k = 0; k < np; k++) {
1547  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncol2 + k] +=
1548  transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[bId_np_j * np + k];
1549  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncol2 + k] -=
1550  transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[eId_np_j * np + k];
1551  dFdXsU[(i + 1) * ncol2 + k] += Akd * bk.dKr_dS[uId_np_j * np + k] / mu * xi * xij * dP;
1552  }
1553  // dxij
1554  for (USI k = 0; k < nc; k++) {
1555  rhox = bk.rhox[uId_np_j * nc + k];
1556  xix = bk.xix[uId_np_j * nc + k];
1557  mux = bk.mux[uId_np_j * nc + k];
1558  tmp = -transIJ * rhoWghtU * rhox * dGamma;
1559  tmp += transJ * xix * xij * dP;
1560  tmp += -transIJ * mux / mu * dP;
1561  dFdXsU[(i + 1) * ncol2 + np + j * nc + k] += tmp;
1562  dFdXsD[(i + 1) * ncol2 + np + j * nc + k] += -transIJ * rhoWghtD * bk.rhox[dId_np_j * nc + k] * dGamma;
1563  }
1564  dFdXsU[(i + 1) * ncol2 + np + j * nc + i] += transJ * xi * dP;
1565  }
1566  }
1567 
1568  // Assemble
1569  bmat = dFdXpB;
1570  DaABpbC(ncol, ncol, ncol2, 1, dFdXsB.data(), &bk.dSec_dPri[bId * bsize2], 1,
1571  bmat.data());
1572  Dscalar(bsize, dt, bmat.data());
1573  // Begin - Begin -- add
1574  ls.AddDiag(bId, bmat);
1575  // End - Begin -- insert
1576  Dscalar(bsize, -1, bmat.data());
1577  ls.NewOffDiag(eId, bId, bmat);
1578 
1579 #ifdef OCP_NANCHECK
1580  if (!CheckNan(bmat.size(), &bmat[0])) {
1581  OCP_ABORT("INF or INF in bmat !");
1582  }
1583 #endif
1584 
1585  // End
1586  bmat = dFdXpE;
1587  DaABpbC(ncol, ncol, ncol2, 1, dFdXsE.data(), &bk.dSec_dPri[eId * bsize2], 1,
1588  bmat.data());
1589  Dscalar(bsize, dt, bmat.data());
1590  // Begin - End -- insert
1591  ls.NewOffDiag(bId, eId, bmat);
1592  // End - End -- add
1593  Dscalar(bsize, -1, bmat.data());
1594  ls.AddDiag(eId, bmat);
1595 
1596 #ifdef OCP_NANCHECK
1597  if (!CheckNan(bmat.size(), &bmat[0])) {
1598  OCP_ABORT("INF or INF in bmat !");
1599  }
1600 #endif
1601  }
1602 }

1605 void IsoT_FIM::AssembleMatBulksNew(LinearSystem& ls, const Reservoir& rs, const OCP_DBL& dt) const
1606 {
1607  const Bulk& bk = rs.bulk;

1609  const OCP_USI nb = bk.numBulk;
1610  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
1611  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
1612  const USI ncol = nc + 1;
1613  const USI ncol2 = np * nc + np;
1614  const USI bsize = ncol * ncol;
1615  const USI bsize2 = ncol * ncol2;
1616  const USI lendSdP = bk.maxLendSdP;
1617 
1618  ls.AddDim(nb);
1619 
1620  vector<OCP_DBL> bmat(bsize, 0);

1624  }

1627  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {

1629  }
1630  ls.NewDiag(n, bmat);

1636  vector<OCP_DBL> dFdXpB(bsize, 0);
1637  vector<OCP_DBL> dFdXpE(bsize, 0);

1639  vector<OCP_DBL> dFdXsE(bsize2, 0);

1642  OCP_BOOL phaseExistU;
1643  vector<OCP_BOOL> phasedS_B(np, OCP_FALSE);

1647  USI ncolB, ncolE;
1648

1650  OCP_USI bId_np_j, eId_np_j, uId_np_j;
1651  OCP_DBL kr, mu, xi, xij, rhoP, xiP, muP, rhox, xix, mux;
1652  OCP_DBL dP, dGamma;
1653  OCP_DBL tmp;
1654 
1655  for (OCP_USI c = 0; c < conn.numConn; c++) {
1656  bId = conn.iteratorConn[c].BId();
1657  eId = conn.iteratorConn[c].EId();
1658  Akd = CONV1 * CONV2 * conn.iteratorConn[c].Area();
1659  fill(dFdXpB.begin(), dFdXpB.end(), 0.0);
1660  fill(dFdXpE.begin(), dFdXpE.end(), 0.0);
1661  fill(dFdXsB.begin(), dFdXsB.end(), 0.0);
1662  fill(dFdXsE.begin(), dFdXsE.end(), 0.0);
1663  dGamma = GRAVITY_FACTOR * (bk.depth[bId] - bk.depth[eId]);
1664 
1665  USI jxB = 0;
1666  USI jxE = 0;
1667  ncolB = 0;
1668  ncolE = 0;

1671  phaseExistB[j] = bk.phaseExist[bId * np + j];
1672  phaseExistE[j] = bk.phaseExist[eId * np + j];
1673  phasedS_B[j] = bk.pSderExist[bId * np + j];
1674  phasedS_E[j] = bk.pSderExist[eId * np + j];
1675  if (phasedS_B[j]) jxB++;
1676  if (phasedS_E[j]) jxE++;
1677  pVnumComB[j] = bk.pVnumCom[bId * np + j];
1678  pVnumComE[j] = bk.pVnumCom[eId * np + j];
1679  ncolB += pVnumComB[j];
1680  ncolE += pVnumComE[j];
1681  }
1682  ncolB += jxB;
1683  ncolE += jxE;
1684 
1685  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
1686  uId = conn.upblock[c * np + j];
1687 
1688  phaseExistU = (uId == bId ? phaseExistB[j] : phaseExistE[j]);
1689  if (!phaseExistU) {
1690  jxB += pVnumComB[j];
1691  jxE += pVnumComE[j];
1692  continue;
1693  }
1694 
1695  bId_np_j = bId * np + j;
1696  eId_np_j = eId * np + j;
1697  uId_np_j = uId * np + j;
1698  dP = bk.Pj[bId_np_j] - bk.Pj[eId_np_j]
1699  - conn.upblock_Rho[c * np + j] * dGamma;
1700  xi = bk.xi[uId_np_j];
1701  kr = bk.kr[uId_np_j];
1702  mu = bk.mu[uId_np_j];
1703  muP = bk.muP[uId_np_j];
1704  xiP = bk.xiP[uId_np_j];
1705  rhoP = bk.rhoP[uId_np_j];
1706  transJ = Akd * kr / mu;
1707 
1708  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
1709  xij = bk.xij[uId_np_j * nc + i];
1710  transIJ = xij * xi * transJ;
1711 
1712  // Pressure -- Primary var
1713  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] += transIJ;
1714  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] -= transIJ;
1715 
1716  tmp = xij * transJ * xiP * dP;
1717  tmp += -transIJ * muP / mu * dP;
1718  if (!phaseExistE[j]) {
1719  tmp += transIJ * (-rhoP * dGamma);
1720  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] += tmp;
1721  } else if (!phaseExistB[j]) {
1722  tmp += transIJ * (-rhoP * dGamma);
1723  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] += tmp;
1724  } else {
1725  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] +=
1726  transIJ * (-bk.rhoP[bId_np_j] * dGamma) / 2;
1727  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] +=
1728  transIJ * (-bk.rhoP[eId_np_j] * dGamma) / 2;
1729  if (bId == uId) {
1730  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] += tmp;
1731  } else {
1732  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] += tmp;
1733  }
1734  }
1735 
1736  // Second var
1737  USI j1SB = 0;
1738  USI j1SE = 0;
1739  if (bId == uId) {
1740  // Saturation
1741  for (USI j1 = 0; j1 < np; j1++) {
1742  if (phasedS_B[j1]) {
1743  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + j1SB] +=
1744  transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[bId_np_j * np + j1];
1745  tmp = Akd * xij * xi / mu *
1746  bk.dKr_dS[uId_np_j * np + j1] * dP;
1747  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + j1SB] += tmp;
1748  j1SB++;
1749  }
1750  if (phasedS_E[j1]) {
1751  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + j1SE] -=
1752  transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[eId_np_j * np + j1];
1753  j1SE++;
1754  }
1755  }
1756  // Cij
1757  if (!phaseExistE[j]) {
1758  for (USI k = 0; k < pVnumComB[j]; k++) {
1759  rhox = bk.rhox[uId_np_j * nc + k];
1760  xix = bk.xix[uId_np_j * nc + k];
1761  mux = bk.mux[uId_np_j * nc + k];
1762  tmp = -transIJ * rhox * dGamma;
1763  tmp += xij * transJ * xix * dP;
1764  tmp += -transIJ * mux / mu * dP;
1765  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + k] += tmp;
1766  }
1767  // WARNING !!!
1768  if (i < pVnumComB[j])
1769  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + i] += xi * transJ * dP;
1770  } else {
1771  for (USI k = 0; k < pVnumComB[j]; k++) {
1772  rhox = bk.rhox[bId_np_j * nc + k] / 2;
1773  xix = bk.xix[uId_np_j * nc + k];
1774  mux = bk.mux[uId_np_j * nc + k];
1775  tmp = -transIJ * rhox * dGamma;
1776  tmp += xij * transJ * xix * dP;
1777  tmp += -transIJ * mux / mu * dP;
1778  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + k] += tmp;
1779  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + jxE + k] +=
1780  -transIJ * bk.rhox[eId_np_j * nc + k] / 2 * dGamma;
1781  }
1782  // WARNING !!!
1783  if (i < pVnumComB[j])
1784  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + i] += xi * transJ * dP;
1785  }
1786  } else {
1787  // Saturation
1788  for (USI j1 = 0; j1 < np; j1++) {
1789  if (phasedS_B[j1]) {
1790  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + j1SB] +=
1791  transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[bId_np_j * np + j1];
1792  j1SB++;
1793  }
1794  if (phasedS_E[j1]) {
1795  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + j1SE] -=
1796  transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[eId_np_j * np + j1];
1797  tmp = Akd * xij * xi / mu *
1798  bk.dKr_dS[uId_np_j * np + j1] * dP;
1799  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + j1SE] += tmp;
1800  j1SE++;
1801  }
1802  }
1803  // Cij
1804  if (!phaseExistB[j]) {
1805  for (USI k = 0; k < pVnumComE[j]; k++) {
1806  rhox = bk.rhox[uId_np_j * nc + k];
1807  xix = bk.xix[uId_np_j * nc + k];
1808  mux = bk.mux[uId_np_j * nc + k];
1809  tmp = -transIJ * rhox * dGamma;
1810  tmp += xij * transJ * xix * dP;
1811  tmp += -transIJ * mux / mu * dP;
1812  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + jxE + k] += tmp;
1813  }
1814  // WARNING !!!
1815  if (i < pVnumComE[j])
1816  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + jxE + i] += xi * transJ * dP;
1817  } else {
1818  for (USI k = 0; k < pVnumComE[j]; k++) {
1819  rhox = bk.rhox[eId_np_j * nc + k] / 2;
1820  xix = bk.xix[uId_np_j * nc + k];
1821  mux = bk.mux[uId_np_j * nc + k];
1822  tmp = -transIJ * rhox * dGamma;
1823  tmp += xij * transJ * xix * dP;
1824  tmp += -transIJ * mux / mu * dP;
1825  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + jxE + k] += tmp;
1826  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + k] +=
1827  -transIJ * bk.rhox[bId_np_j * nc + k] / 2 * dGamma;
1828  }
1829  // WARNING !!!
1830  if (i < pVnumComE[j])
1831  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + jxE + i] += xi * transJ * dP;
1832  }
1833  }
1834  }
1835  jxB += pVnumComB[j];
1836  jxE += pVnumComE[j];
1837  }
1838 
1839  // Assemble
1840  bmat = dFdXpB;
1841  DaABpbC(ncol, ncol, ncolB, 1, dFdXsB.data(), &bk.dSec_dPri[bId * lendSdP],
1842  1, bmat.data());
1843  Dscalar(bsize, dt, bmat.data());
1844  // Begin - Begin -- add
1845  ls.AddDiag(bId, bmat);
1846  // End - Begin -- insert
1847  Dscalar(bsize, -1, bmat.data());
1848  ls.NewOffDiag(eId, bId, bmat);
1849 
1850 #ifdef OCP_NANCHECK
1851  if (!CheckNan(bmat.size(), &bmat[0])) {
1852  OCP_ABORT("INF or NAN in bmat !");
1853  }
1854 #endif
1855 
1856  bmat = dFdXpE;
1857  DaABpbC(ncol, ncol, ncolE, 1, dFdXsE.data(), &bk.dSec_dPri[eId * lendSdP],
1858  1, bmat.data());
1859 
1860  Dscalar(bsize, dt, bmat.data());
1861  // Begin - End -- insert
1862  ls.NewOffDiag(bId, eId, bmat);
1863  // End - End -- add
1864  Dscalar(bsize, -1, bmat.data());
1865  ls.AddDiag(eId, bmat);
1866 
1867 #ifdef OCP_NANCHECK
1868  if (!CheckNan(bmat.size(), &bmat[0])) {
1869  OCP_ABORT("INF or INF in bmat !");
1870  }
1871 #endif
1872  }
1873 }

1875 
1876 void IsoT_FIM::AssembleMatBulksNewS(LinearSystem& ls,
1877  const Reservoir& rs,
1878  const OCP_DBL& dt) const
1879 {
1880 
1881  const Bulk& bk = rs.bulk;
1882  const BulkConn& conn = rs.conn;
1883  const OCP_USI nb = bk.numCom;
1884  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
1885  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
1886  const USI ncol = nc + 1;
1887  const USI ncol2 = np * nc + np;
1888  const USI bsize = ncol * ncol;
1889  const USI bsize2 = ncol * ncol2;
1890  const USI lendSdP = bk.maxLendSdP;
1891 
1892  ls.AddDim(nb);
1893 
1894  vector<OCP_DBL> bmat(bsize, 0);
1895  // Accumulation term
1896  for (USI i = 1; i < ncol; i++) {
1897  bmat[i * ncol + i] = 1;
1898  }
1899  for (OCP_USI n = 0; n < nb; n++) {
1900  bmat[0] = bk.v[n] * bk.poroP[n] - bk.vfP[n];
1901  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
1902  bmat[i + 1] = -bk.vfi[n * nc + i];
1903  }
1904  ls.NewDiag(n, bmat);
1905  }
1906 
1907  // flux term
1908  OCP_DBL Akd;
1909  OCP_DBL transJ, transIJ;
1910  vector<OCP_DBL> dFdXpB(bsize, 0);
1911  vector<OCP_DBL> dFdXpE(bsize, 0);
1912  vector<OCP_DBL> dFdXsB(bsize2, 0);
1913  vector<OCP_DBL> dFdXsE(bsize2, 0);
1914  vector<OCP_BOOL> phaseExistB(np, OCP_FALSE);
1915  vector<OCP_BOOL> phaseExistE(np, OCP_FALSE);
1916  OCP_BOOL phaseExistU;
1917  vector<USI> pEnumComB(np, 0);
1918  vector<USI> pEnumComE(np, 0);
1919  USI ncolB, ncolE;
1920 
1921  OCP_USI bId, eId, uId;
1922  OCP_USI bId_np_j, eId_np_j, uId_np_j;
1923  OCP_DBL kr, mu, xi, xij, rhoP, xiP, muP, rhox, xix, mux;
1924  OCP_DBL dP, dGamma;
1925  OCP_DBL tmp;
1926  OCP_DBL wghtb, wghte;
1927 
1928  for (OCP_USI c = 0; c < conn.numConn; c++) {
1929  bId = conn.iteratorConn[c].BId();
1930  eId = conn.iteratorConn[c].EId();
1931  Akd = CONV1 * CONV2 * conn.iteratorConn[c].Area();
1932  fill(dFdXpB.begin(), dFdXpB.end(), 0.0);
1933  fill(dFdXpE.begin(), dFdXpE.end(), 0.0);
1934  fill(dFdXsB.begin(), dFdXsB.end(), 0.0);
1935  fill(dFdXsE.begin(), dFdXsE.end(), 0.0);
1936  dGamma = GRAVITY_FACTOR * (bk.depth[bId] - bk.depth[eId]);
1937 
1938  const USI npB = bk.phaseNum[bId];
1939  ncolB = npB;
1940  const USI npE = bk.phaseNum[eId];
1941  ncolE = npE;
1942 
1943  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
1944  phaseExistB[j] = bk.phaseExist[bId * np + j];
1945  phaseExistE[j] = bk.phaseExist[eId * np + j];
1946  pEnumComB[j] = bk.pVnumCom[bId * np + j];
1947  pEnumComE[j] = bk.pVnumCom[eId * np + j];
1948  ncolB += pEnumComB[j];
1949  ncolE += pEnumComE[j];
1950  }
1951 
1952  USI jxB = npB;
1953  USI jxE = npE;
1954  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
1955  uId = conn.upblock[c * np + j];
1956 
1957  phaseExistU = (uId == bId ? phaseExistB[j] : phaseExistE[j]);
1958  if (!phaseExistU) {
1959  jxB += pEnumComB[j];
1960  jxE += pEnumComE[j];
1961  continue;
1962  }
1963 
1964  bId_np_j = bId * np + j;
1965  eId_np_j = eId * np + j;
1966  uId_np_j = uId * np + j;
1967  dP = bk.Pj[bId_np_j] - bk.Pj[eId_np_j] -
1968  conn.upblock_Rho[c * np + j] * dGamma;
1969  xi = bk.xi[uId_np_j];
1970  kr = bk.kr[uId_np_j];
1971  mu = bk.mu[uId_np_j];
1972  muP = bk.muP[uId_np_j];
1973  xiP = bk.xiP[uId_np_j];
1974  rhoP = bk.rhoP[uId_np_j];
1975  transJ = Akd * kr / mu;
1976 
1977  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
1978  xij = bk.xij[uId_np_j * nc + i];
1979  transIJ = xij * xi * transJ;
1980 
1981  // Pressure -- Primary var
1982  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] += transIJ;
1983  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] -= transIJ;
1984 
1985  tmp = xij * transJ * xiP * dP;
1986  tmp += -transIJ * muP / mu * dP;
1987  if (!phaseExistE[j]) {
1988  tmp += transIJ * (-rhoP * dGamma);
1989  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] += tmp;
1990  } else if (!phaseExistB[j]) {
1991  tmp += transIJ * (-rhoP * dGamma);
1992  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] += tmp;
1993  } else {
1994  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] +=
1995  transIJ * dGamma *
1996  (-bk.rhoP[bId_np_j] * bk.S[bId_np_j]) /
1997  (bk.S[bId_np_j] + bk.S[eId_np_j]);
1998  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] +=
1999  transIJ * dGamma *
2000  (-bk.rhoP[eId_np_j] * bk.S[eId_np_j]) /
2001  (bk.S[bId_np_j] + bk.S[eId_np_j]);
2002  if (bId == uId) {
2003  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] += tmp;
2004  } else {
2005  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] += tmp;
2006  }
2007  }
2008 
2009  // Second var
2010  USI j1SB = 0;
2011  USI j1SE = 0;
2012  if (bId == uId) {
2013  // Saturation
2014  for (USI j1 = 0; j1 < np; j1++) {
2015 
2016  wghtb = 0;
2017  wghte = 0;
2018  if (j1 == j && phaseExistE[j]) {
2019  tmp = -dGamma / ((bk.S[bId_np_j] + bk.S[eId_np_j]) *
2020  (bk.S[bId_np_j] + bk.S[eId_np_j]));
2021  wghtb = tmp * bk.rho[bId_np_j] * bk.S[eId_np_j];
2022  wghte = tmp * bk.rho[eId_np_j] * bk.S[bId_np_j];
2023  }
2024 
2025  if (phaseExistB[j1]) {
2026  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + j1SB] +=
2027  transIJ * (bk.dPcj_dS[bId_np_j * np + j1] + wghtb);
2028  tmp = Akd * xij * xi / mu *
2029  bk.dKr_dS[uId_np_j * np + j1] * dP;
2030  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + j1SB] += tmp;
2031  j1SB++;
2032  }
2033  if (phaseExistE[j1]) {
2034  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + j1SE] -=
2035  transIJ * (bk.dPcj_dS[eId_np_j * np + j1] + wghte);
2036  j1SE++;
2037  }
2038  }
2039  // Cij
2040  if (!phaseExistE[j]) {
2041  for (USI k = 0; k < pEnumComB[j]; k++) {
2042  rhox = bk.rhox[uId_np_j * nc + k];
2043  xix = bk.xix[uId_np_j * nc + k];
2044  mux = bk.mux[uId_np_j * nc + k];
2045  tmp = -transIJ * rhox * dGamma;
2046  tmp += xij * transJ * xix * dP;
2047  tmp += -transIJ * mux / mu * dP;
2048  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + k] += tmp;
2049  }
2050  // WARNING !!!
2051  if (i < pEnumComB[j])
2052  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + i] += xi * transJ * dP;
2053  } else {
2054  wghtb = bk.S[bId_np_j] /
2055  (bk.S[bId_np_j] + bk.S[eId_np_j]);
2056  wghte = bk.S[eId_np_j] /
2057  (bk.S[bId_np_j] + bk.S[eId_np_j]);
2058  for (USI k = 0; k < pEnumComB[j]; k++) {
2059  rhox = bk.rhox[bId_np_j * nc + k] * wghtb;
2060  xix = bk.xix[uId_np_j * nc + k];
2061  mux = bk.mux[uId_np_j * nc + k];
2062  tmp = -transIJ * rhox * dGamma;
2063  tmp += xij * transJ * xix * dP;
2064  tmp += -transIJ * mux / mu * dP;
2065  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + k] += tmp;
2066  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + jxE + k] +=
2067  -transIJ * dGamma * bk.rhox[eId_np_j * nc + k] *
2068  wghte;
2069  }
2070  // WARNING !!!
2071  if (i < pEnumComB[j])
2072  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + i] += xi * transJ * dP;
2073  }
2074  } else {
2075  // Saturation
2076  for (USI j1 = 0; j1 < np; j1++) {
2077 
2078  wghtb = 0;
2079  wghte = 0;
2080  if (j1 == j && phaseExistB[j]) {
2081  tmp = -dGamma / ((bk.S[bId_np_j] + bk.S[eId_np_j]) *
2082  (bk.S[bId_np_j] + bk.S[eId_np_j]));
2083  wghtb = tmp * bk.rho[bId_np_j] * bk.S[eId_np_j];
2084  wghte = tmp * bk.rho[eId_np_j] * bk.S[bId_np_j];
2085  }
2086 
2087  if (phaseExistB[j1]) {
2088  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + j1SB] +=
2089  transIJ * (bk.dPcj_dS[bId_np_j * np + j1] + wghtb);
2090  j1SB++;
2091  }
2092  if (phaseExistE[j1]) {
2093  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + j1SE] -=
2094  transIJ * (bk.dPcj_dS[eId_np_j * np + j1] + wghte);
2095  tmp = Akd * xij * xi / mu *
2096  bk.dKr_dS[uId_np_j * np + j1] * dP;
2097  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + j1SE] += tmp;
2098  j1SE++;
2099  }
2100  }
2101  // Cij
2102  if (!phaseExistB[j]) {
2103  for (USI k = 0; k < pEnumComE[j]; k++) {
2104  rhox = bk.rhox[uId_np_j * nc + k];
2105  xix = bk.xix[uId_np_j * nc + k];
2106  mux = bk.mux[uId_np_j * nc + k];
2107  tmp = -transIJ * rhox * dGamma;
2108  tmp += xij * transJ * xix * dP;
2109  tmp += -transIJ * mux / mu * dP;
2110  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + jxE + k] += tmp;
2111  }
2112  // WARNING !!!
2113  if (i < pEnumComE[j])
2114  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + jxE + i] += xi * transJ * dP;
2115  } else {
2116  wghtb = bk.S[bId_np_j] /
2117  (bk.S[bId_np_j] + bk.S[eId_np_j]);
2118  wghte = bk.S[eId_np_j] /
2119  (bk.S[bId_np_j] + bk.S[eId_np_j]);
2120  for (USI k = 0; k < pEnumComE[j]; k++) {
2121  rhox = bk.rhox[eId_np_j * nc + k] * wghte;
2122  xix = bk.xix[uId_np_j * nc + k];
2123  mux = bk.mux[uId_np_j * nc + k];
2124  tmp = -transIJ * rhox * dGamma;
2125  tmp += xij * transJ * xix * dP;
2126  tmp += -transIJ * mux / mu * dP;
2127  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + jxE + k] += tmp;
2128  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + k] +=
2129  -transIJ * dGamma * bk.rhox[bId_np_j * nc + k] *

2131  }
2132  // WARNING !!!
2133  if (i < pEnumComE[j])
2134  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + jxE + i] += xi * transJ * dP;
2135  }
2136  }
2137  }
2138  jxB += pEnumComB[j];
2139  jxE += pEnumComE[j];
2140  }

2143  bmat = dFdXpB;

2211 void IsoT_FIM::AssembleMatInjWells(LinearSystem& ls,
2212  const Bulk& bk,
2213  const Well& wl,
2214  const OCP_DBL& dt) const
2215 {
2216  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
2217  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
2218  const USI ncol = nc + 1;
2219  const USI ncol2 = np * nc + np;
2220  const USI bsize = ncol * ncol;
2221  const USI bsize2 = ncol * ncol2;
2222  OCP_USI n_np_j;
2223 
2224  vector<OCP_DBL> bmat(bsize, 0);
2225  vector<OCP_DBL> bmat2(bsize, 0);
2226  vector<OCP_DBL> dQdXpB(bsize, 0);
2227  vector<OCP_DBL> dQdXpW(bsize, 0);
2228  vector<OCP_DBL> dQdXsB(bsize2, 0);
2229 
2230  OCP_DBL mu, muP, dP, transIJ;
2231 
2232  const OCP_USI wId = ls.AddDim(1) - 1;
2233  ls.NewDiag(wId, bmat);
2234 
2235  for (USI p = 0; p < wl.PerfNum(); p++) {
2236  const OCP_USI n = wl.PerfLocation(p);
2237  fill(dQdXpB.begin(), dQdXpB.end(), 0.0);
2238  fill(dQdXpW.begin(), dQdXpW.end(), 0.0);
2239  fill(dQdXsB.begin(), dQdXsB.end(), 0.0);
2240 
2241  dP = bk.P[n] - wl.BHP() - wl.DG(p);
2242 
2243  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
2244  n_np_j = n * np + j;
2245  if (!bk.phaseExist[n_np_j]) continue;
2246 
2247  mu = bk.mu[n_np_j];
2248  muP = bk.muP[n_np_j];
2249 
2250  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
2251  // dQ / dP
2252  transIJ = wl.PerfTransj(p, j) * wl.PerfXi(p) * wl.InjZi(i);
2253  dQdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] += transIJ * (1 - dP * muP / mu);
2254  dQdXpW[(i + 1) * ncol] += -transIJ;
2255 
2256  // dQ / dS
2257  for (USI k = 0; k < np; k++) {
2258  dQdXsB[(i + 1) * ncol2 + k] +=
2259  CONV1 * wl.PerfWI(p) * wl.PerfMultiplier(p) * wl.PerfXi(p) *
2260  wl.InjZi(i) * bk.dKr_dS[n_np_j * np + k] * dP / mu;
2261  }
2262  // dQ / dxij
2263  for (USI k = 0; k < nc; k++) {
2264  dQdXsB[(i + 1) * ncol2 + np + j * nc + k] +=
2265  -transIJ * dP / mu * bk.mux[n_np_j * nc + k];
2266  }
2267  }
2268  }
2269 
2270  // Bulk to Well
2271  bmat = dQdXpB;
2272  DaABpbC(ncol, ncol, ncol2, 1, dQdXsB.data(), &bk.dSec_dPri[n * bsize2], 1,
2273  bmat.data());
2274  Dscalar(bsize, dt, bmat.data());
2275  // Bulk - Bulk -- add
2276  ls.AddDiag(n, bmat);
2277 
2278  // Bulk - Well -- insert
2279  bmat = dQdXpW;
2280  Dscalar(bsize, dt, bmat.data());
2281  ls.NewOffDiag(n, wId, bmat);
2282 
2283  // Well
2284  switch (wl.OptMode()) {
2285  case RATE_MODE:
2286  case ORATE_MODE:
2287  case GRATE_MODE:
2288  case WRATE_MODE:
2289  case LRATE_MODE:
2290  // Well - Well -- add
2291  fill(bmat.begin(), bmat.end(), 0.0);
2292  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
2293  bmat[0] += dQdXpW[(i + 1) * ncol];
2294  bmat[(i + 1) * ncol + i + 1] = 1;
2295  }
2296  ls.AddDiag(wId, bmat);
2297 
2298  // Well - Bulk -- insert
2299  bmat = dQdXpB;
2300  DaABpbC(ncol, ncol, ncol2, 1, dQdXsB.data(),
2301  &bk.dSec_dPri[n * bsize2], 1, bmat.data());
2302  fill(bmat2.begin(), bmat2.end(), 0.0);
2303  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
2304  Daxpy(ncol, 1.0, bmat.data() + (i + 1) * ncol, bmat2.data());
2305  }
2306  ls.NewOffDiag(wId, n, bmat2);
2307  break;
2308 
2309  case BHP_MODE:
2310  // Well - Well -- add
2311  fill(bmat.begin(), bmat.end(), 0.0);
2312  for (USI i = 0; i < ncol; i++) {
2313  bmat[i * ncol + i] = 1;
2314  }
2315  ls.AddDiag(wId, bmat);
2316 
2317  // Well - Bulk -- insert
2318  fill(bmat.begin(), bmat.end(), 0.0);
2319  ls.NewOffDiag(wId, n, bmat);
2320  break;
2321 
2322  default:
2323  OCP_ABORT("Wrong Well Opt mode!");
2324  break;
2325  }
2326  }

2330 void IsoT_FIM::AssembleMatProdWells(LinearSystem& ls,
2331  const Bulk& bk,
2332  const Well& wl,
2333  const OCP_DBL& dt) const
2334 {
2335  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
2336  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
2337  const USI ncol = nc + 1;
2338  const USI ncol2 = np * nc + np;
2339  const USI bsize = ncol * ncol;
2340  const USI bsize2 = ncol * ncol2;
2341  OCP_USI n_np_j;
2342 
2343  vector<OCP_DBL> bmat(bsize, 0);
2344  vector<OCP_DBL> bmat2(bsize, 0);
2345  vector<OCP_DBL> dQdXpB(bsize, 0);
2346  vector<OCP_DBL> dQdXpW(bsize, 0);
2347  vector<OCP_DBL> dQdXsB(bsize2, 0);
2348 
2349  OCP_DBL xij, xi, mu, muP, xiP, dP,transIJ, tmp;
2350 
2351  const OCP_USI wId = ls.AddDim(1) - 1;
2352  ls.NewDiag(wId, bmat);
2353 
2354  // Set Prod Weight
2355  if (wl.OptMode() != BHP_MODE) wl.CalProdWeight(bk);
2356 
2357  for (USI p = 0; p < wl.PerfNum(); p++) {
2358  const OCP_USI n = wl.PerfLocation(p);
2359  fill(dQdXpB.begin(), dQdXpB.end(), 0.0);
2360  fill(dQdXpW.begin(), dQdXpW.end(), 0.0);
2361  fill(dQdXsB.begin(), dQdXsB.end(), 0.0);
2362 
2363  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
2364  n_np_j = n * np + j;
2365  if (!bk.phaseExist[n_np_j]) continue;
2366 
2367  dP = bk.Pj[n_np_j] - wl.BHP() - wl.DG(p);
2368  xi = bk.xi[n_np_j];
2369  mu = bk.mu[n_np_j];
2370  muP = bk.muP[n_np_j];
2371  xiP = bk.xiP[n_np_j];
2372 
2373  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
2374  xij = bk.xij[n_np_j * nc + i];
2375  // dQ / dP
2376  transIJ = wl.PerfTransj(p, j) * xi * xij;
2377  dQdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] +=
2378  transIJ * (1 - dP * muP / mu) + dP * wl.PerfTransj(p, j) * xij * xiP;
2379  dQdXpW[(i + 1) * ncol] += -transIJ;
2380 
2381  // dQ / dS
2382  for (USI k = 0; k < np; k++) {
2383  tmp = CONV1 * wl.PerfWI(p) * wl.PerfMultiplier(p) * dP / mu * xi * xij *
2384  bk.dKr_dS[n_np_j * np + k];
2385  // capillary pressure
2386  tmp += transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[n_np_j * np + k];
2387  dQdXsB[(i + 1) * ncol2 + k] += tmp;
2388  }
2389  // dQ / dCij
2390  for (USI k = 0; k < nc; k++) {
2391  tmp = dP * wl.PerfTransj(p, j) * xij *
2392  (bk.xix[n_np_j * nc + k] -
2393  xi / mu * bk.mux[n_np_j * nc + k]);
2394  dQdXsB[(i + 1) * ncol2 + np + j * nc + k] += tmp;
2395  }
2396  dQdXsB[(i + 1) * ncol2 + np + j * nc + i] +=
2397  wl.PerfTransj(p, j) * xi * dP;
2398  }
2399  }
2400 
2401  // Bulk - Bulk -- add
2402  bmat = dQdXpB;
2403  DaABpbC(ncol, ncol, ncol2, 1, dQdXsB.data(), &bk.dSec_dPri[n * bsize2], 1,
2404  bmat.data());
2405 
2406  Dscalar(bsize, dt, bmat.data());
2407  ls.AddDiag(n, bmat);
2408 
2409  // Bulk - Well -- insert
2410  bmat = dQdXpW;
2411  Dscalar(bsize, dt, bmat.data());
2412  ls.NewOffDiag(n, wId, bmat);
2413 
2414  // Well
2415  switch (wl.OptMode()) {
2416  case RATE_MODE:
2417  case ORATE_MODE:
2418  case GRATE_MODE:
2419  case WRATE_MODE:
2420  case LRATE_MODE:
2421  // Well - Well -- add
2422  fill(bmat.begin(), bmat.end(), 0.0);
2423  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
2424  bmat[0] += dQdXpW[(i + 1) * ncol] * wl.ProdWeight(i);
2425  bmat[(i + 1) * ncol + i + 1] = 1;
2426  }
2427  ls.AddDiag(wId, bmat);
2428 
2429  // Well - Bulk -- insert
2430  bmat = dQdXpB;
2431  DaABpbC(ncol, ncol, ncol2, 1, dQdXsB.data(),
2432  &bk.dSec_dPri[n * bsize2], 1, bmat.data());
2433  fill(bmat2.begin(), bmat2.end(), 0.0);
2434  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
2435  Daxpy(ncol, wl.ProdWeight(i), bmat.data() + (i + 1) * ncol,
2436  bmat2.data());
2437  }
2438  ls.NewOffDiag(wId, n, bmat2);
2439  break;
2440 
2441  case BHP_MODE:
2442  // Well - Well -- add
2443  fill(bmat.begin(), bmat.end(), 0.0);
2444  for (USI i = 0; i < ncol; i++) {
2445  bmat[i * ncol + i] = 1;
2446  }
2447  ls.AddDiag(wId, bmat);
2448 
2449  // Well - Bulk -- insert
2450  fill(bmat.begin(), bmat.end(), 0.0);
2451  ls.NewOffDiag(wId, n, bmat);
2452  break;
2453 
2454  default:
2455  OCP_ABORT("Wrong Well Opt mode!");
2456  break;
2457  }
2458  }

2657  fill(dQdXpW.begin(), dQdXpW.end(), 0.0);
2658  fill(dQdXsB.begin(), dQdXsB.end(), 0.0);
2659 
2660  USI jxB = 0;
2661  ncolB = 0;
2662  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
2663  phaseExistB[j] = bk.phaseExist[n * np + j];
2664  phasedS_B[j] = bk.pSderExist[n * np + j];
2665  if (phasedS_B[j]) jxB++;
2666  pVnumComB[j] = bk.pVnumCom[n * np + j];
2667  ncolB += pVnumComB[j];
2668  }
2669  ncolB += jxB;
2670 
2671  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
2672 
2673  if (!phaseExistB[j]) {
2674  jxB += pVnumComB[j];
2675  continue;
2676  }
2677 
2678  n_np_j = n * np + j;
2679  dP = bk.Pj[n_np_j] - wl.BHP() - wl.DG(p);
2680  xi = bk.xi[n_np_j];
2681  mu = bk.mu[n_np_j];
2682  muP = bk.muP[n_np_j];
2683  xiP = bk.xiP[n_np_j];
2684 
2685  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
2686  xij = bk.xij[n_np_j * nc + i];
2687  // dQ / dP
2688  transIJ = wl.PerfTransj(p, j) * xi * xij;
2689  dQdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] +=
2690  transIJ * (1 - dP * muP / mu) + dP * wl.PerfTransj(p, j) * xij * xiP;
2691  dQdXpW[(i + 1) * ncol] += -transIJ;
2692 
2693  // dQ / dS
2694  USI j1B = 0;
2695  for (USI j1 = 0; j1 < np; j1++) {
2696  if (phasedS_B[j1]) {
2697  tmp = CONV1 * wl.PerfWI(p) * wl.PerfMultiplier(p) * dP / mu * xi *
2698  xij * bk.dKr_dS[n_np_j * np + j1];
2699  // capillary pressure
2700  tmp += transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[n_np_j * np + j1];
2701  dQdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + j1B] += tmp;
2702  j1B++;
2703  }
2704  }
2705 
2706  for (USI k = 0; k < pVnumComB[j]; k++) {
2707  tmp = dP * wl.PerfTransj(p, j) * xij *
2708  (bk.xix[n_np_j * nc + k] -
2709  xi / mu * bk.mux[n_np_j * nc + k]);
2710  dQdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + k] += tmp;
2711  }
2712  // WARNING !!!
2713  if (i < pVnumComB[j])
2714  dQdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + i] += wl.PerfTransj(p, j) * xi * dP;
2715  }
2716  jxB += pVnumComB[j];
2717  }
2718  // Bulk - Bulk -- add
2719  bmat = dQdXpB;
2720  DaABpbC(ncol, ncol, ncolB, 1, dQdXsB.data(), &bk.dSec_dPri[n * lendSdP], 1,
2721  bmat.data());
2722  Dscalar(bsize, dt, bmat.data());
2723  ls.AddDiag(n, bmat);
2724  // Bulk - Well -- insert
2725  bmat = dQdXpW;
2726  Dscalar(bsize, dt, bmat.data());
2727  ls.NewOffDiag(n, wId, bmat);
2728 
2729  // Well
2730  switch (wl.OptMode()) {
2731  case RATE_MODE:
2732  case ORATE_MODE:
2733  case GRATE_MODE:
2734  case WRATE_MODE:
2735  case LRATE_MODE:
2736  // Well - Well -- add
2737  fill(bmat.begin(), bmat.end(), 0.0);
2738  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
2739  bmat[0] += dQdXpW[(i + 1) * ncol] * wl.ProdWeight(i);
2740  bmat[(i + 1) * ncol + i + 1] = 1;
2741  }
2742  ls.AddDiag(wId, bmat);
2743 
2744  // Well - Bulk -- insert
2745  bmat = dQdXpB;
2746  DaABpbC(ncol, ncol, ncolB, 1, dQdXsB.data(),
2747  &bk.dSec_dPri[n * lendSdP], 1, bmat.data());
2748  fill(bmat2.begin(), bmat2.end(), 0.0);
2749  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
2750  Daxpy(ncol, wl.ProdWeight(i), bmat.data() + (i + 1) * ncol,
2751  bmat2.data());
2752  }
2753  ls.NewOffDiag(wId, n, bmat2);
2754  break;
2755 
2756  case BHP_MODE:
2757  // Well - Well -- add
2758  fill(bmat.begin(), bmat.end(), 0.0);
2759  for (USI i = 0; i < ncol; i++) {
2760  bmat[i * ncol + i] = 1;
2761  }
2762  ls.AddDiag(wId, bmat);
2763 
2764  // Well - Bulk -- insert
2765  fill(bmat.begin(), bmat.end(), 0.0);
2766  ls.NewOffDiag(wId, n, bmat);
2767  break;
2768 
2769  default:
2770  OCP_ABORT("Wrong Well Opt mode!");
2771  break;
2772  }
2773  }
2774 }

2777 void IsoT_FIM::GetSolution(Reservoir& rs, const vector<OCP_DBL>& u, const OCPControl& ctrl) const
2778 {
2779  // Bulk
2780  const OCP_DBL dSmaxlim = ctrl.ctrlNR.NRdSmax;
2781  // const OCP_DBL dPmaxlim = ctrl.ctrlNR.NRdPmax;
2782 
2783  Bulk& bk = rs.bulk;
2784  const OCP_USI nb = bk.numBulk;
2785  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
2786  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
2787  const USI row = np * (nc + 1);
2788  const USI col = nc + 1;
2789  vector<OCP_DBL> dtmp(row, 0);
2790  OCP_DBL chopmin = 1;
2791  OCP_DBL choptmp = 0;
2792 
2793  bk.dSNR = bk.S;
2794  bk.NRphaseNum = bk.phaseNum;
2795  bk.NRdPmax = 0;
2796  bk.NRdNmax = 0;
2797 
2798  for (OCP_USI n = 0; n < nb; n++) {
2799  // const vector<OCP_DBL>& scm = satcm[SATNUM[n]];
2800 
2801  chopmin = 1;
2802  // compute the chop
2803  fill(dtmp.begin(), dtmp.end(), 0.0);
2804 
2805 #ifdef OCP_OLD_FIM
2806  DaAxpby(row, col, 1, &bk.dSec_dPri[n * bk.maxLendSdP], u.data() + n * col, 1,
2807  dtmp.data());
2808  const OCP_BOOL newFIM = OCP_FALSE;
2809 #else
2810  DaAxpby(bk.bRowSizedSdP[n], col, 1, &bk.dSec_dPri[n * bk.maxLendSdP], u.data() + n * col,
2811  1, dtmp.data());
2812  const OCP_BOOL newFIM = OCP_TRUE;
2813 #endif // OCP_OLD_FIM
2814 
2815  USI js = 0;
2816  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
2817  if (!bk.pSderExist[n * np + j] && newFIM) {
2818  continue;
2819  }
2820 
2821  choptmp = 1;
2822  if (fabs(dtmp[js]) > dSmaxlim) {
2823  choptmp = dSmaxlim / fabs(dtmp[js]);
2824  }
2825  else if (bk.S[n * np + j] + dtmp[js] < 0.0) {
2826  choptmp = 0.9 * bk.S[n * np + j] / fabs(dtmp[js]);
2827  }
2828 
2829  // if (fabs(S[n_np_j] - scm[j]) > TINY &&
2830  // (S[n_np_j] - scm[j]) / (choptmp * dtmp[js]) < 0)
2831  // choptmp *= min(1.0, -((S[n_np_j] - scm[j]) / (choptmp * dtmp[js])));
2832 
2833  chopmin = min(chopmin, choptmp);
2834  js++;
2835  }
2836 
2837  // dS
2838  js = 0;
2839  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
2840  if (!bk.pSderExist[n * np + j] && newFIM) {
2841  bk.dSNRP[n * np + j] = 0;
2842  continue;
2843  }
2844  bk.dSNRP[n * np + j] = chopmin * dtmp[js];
2845  bk.S[n * np + j] += bk.dSNRP[n * np + j];
2846  js++;
2847  }
2848 
2849  // dxij ---- Compositional model only
2850  if (bk.IfUseEoS()) {
2851  if (bk.phaseNum[n] >= 3) {
2852  // num of Hydroncarbon phase >= 2
2853  OCP_USI bId = 0;
2854  for (USI j = 0; j < 2; j++) {
2855  bId = n * np * nc + j * nc;
2856  for (USI i = 0; i < bk.numComH; i++) {
2857  bk.xij[bId + i] += chopmin * dtmp[js];
2858  js++;
2859  }
2860 #ifdef OCP_OLD_FIM
2861  js++;
2862 #endif // OCP_OLD_FIM
2863  }
2864  }
2865  }
2866 
2867  // dP
2868  OCP_DBL dP = u[n * col];
2869  // choptmp = dPmaxlim / fabs(dP);
2870  // chopmin = min(chopmin, choptmp);
2871  if (fabs(bk.NRdPmax) < fabs(dP)) bk.NRdPmax = dP;
2872  bk.P[n] += dP; // seems better
2873  bk.dPNR[n] = dP;
2874 
2875  // dNi
2876  bk.NRstep[n] = chopmin;
2877  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
2878  bk.dNNR[n * nc + i] = u[n * col + 1 + i] * chopmin;
2879  if (fabs(bk.NRdNmax) < fabs(bk.dNNR[n * nc + i]) / bk.Nt[n])
2880  bk.NRdNmax = bk.dNNR[n * nc + i] / bk.Nt[n];
2881 
2882  bk.Ni[n * nc + i] += bk.dNNR[n * nc + i];
2883 
2884  //if (bk.Ni[n * nc + i] < 0) {
2885  // bk.Ni[n * nc + i] = 1E-20;
2886  //}
2887  }
2888  }
2889 
2890  // Well
2891  OCP_USI wId = nb * col;
2892  for (auto& wl : rs.allWells.wells) {
2893  if (wl.IsOpen()) {
2894  wl.SetBHP(wl.BHP() + u[wId]);
2895  wId += col;
2896  }
2897  }
2898 }

3254 void IsoT_FIMn::AssembleMatBulksNew(LinearSystem& ls,
3255  const Reservoir& rs,
3256  const OCP_DBL& dt) const
3257 {
3258 
3259  const Bulk& bk = rs.bulk;
3260  const BulkConn& conn = rs.conn;
3261  const OCP_USI nb = bk.numBulk;
3262  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
3263  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
3264  const USI ncol = nc + 1;
3265  const USI ncol2 = np * nc + np;
3266  const USI bsize = ncol * ncol;
3267  const USI bsize2 = ncol * ncol2;
3268  const USI lendSdP = bk.maxLendSdP;
3269 
3270  ls.AddDim(nb);
3271 
3272  vector<OCP_DBL> bmat(bsize, 0);
3273  vector<OCP_DBL> tmpb(ncol, 0);
3274 
3275  // Accumulation term
3276  for (USI i = 1; i < ncol; i++) {
3277  bmat[i * ncol + i] = 1;
3278  }
3279  for (OCP_USI n = 0; n < nb; n++) {
3280  bmat[0] = bk.v[n] * bk.poroP[n] - bk.vfP[n];
3281  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
3282  bmat[i + 1] = -bk.vfi[n * nc + i];
3283  }
3284

3286  ls.AddRhs(n * ncol, -bk.resPc[n]);
3287  }
3288 
3289  // flux term
3290  OCP_DBL Akd;
3291  OCP_DBL transJ, transIJ;

3293  vector<OCP_DBL> dFdXpE(bsize, 0);
3294  vector<OCP_DBL> dFdXsB(bsize2, 0);
3295  vector<OCP_DBL> dFdXsE(bsize2, 0);

3302  vector<USI> pVnumComE(np, 0);

3306  OCP_USI bId_np_j, eId_np_j, uId_np_j;
3307  OCP_DBL kr, mu, xi, xij, rhoP, xiP, muP, rhox, xix, mux;
3308  OCP_DBL dP, dGamma;
3309  OCP_DBL tmp;
3310

3312  bId = conn.iteratorConn[c].BId();
3313  eId = conn.iteratorConn[c].EId();
3314  Akd = CONV1 * CONV2 * conn.iteratorConn[c].Area();
3315  fill(dFdXpB.begin(), dFdXpB.end(), 0.0);
3316  fill(dFdXpE.begin(), dFdXpE.end(), 0.0);
3317  fill(dFdXsB.begin(), dFdXsB.end(), 0.0);
3318  fill(dFdXsE.begin(), dFdXsE.end(), 0.0);
3319  dGamma = GRAVITY_FACTOR * (bk.depth[bId] - bk.depth[eId]);
3320 
3321  const USI npB = bk.phaseNum[bId];
3322  const USI npE = bk.phaseNum[eId];
3323 
3324  USI jxB = 0;
3325  USI jxE = 0;
3326  ncolB = 0;
3327  ncolE = 0;
3328  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
3329  phaseExistB[j] = bk.phaseExist[bId * np + j];
3330  phaseExistE[j] = bk.phaseExist[eId * np + j];
3331  phasedS_B[j] = bk.pSderExist[bId * np + j];
3332  phasedS_E[j] = bk.pSderExist[eId * np + j];
3333  if (phasedS_B[j]) jxB++;
3334  if (phasedS_E[j]) jxE++;

3336  pVnumComE[j] = bk.pVnumCom[eId * np + j];
3337  ncolB += pVnumComB[j];
3338  ncolE += pVnumComE[j];
3339  }
3340  ncolB += jxB;
3341  ncolE += jxE;
3342 
3343  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
3344  uId = conn.upblock[c * np + j];
3345 
3346  phaseExistU = (uId == bId ? phaseExistB[j] : phaseExistE[j]);
3347  if (!phaseExistU) {
3348  jxB += pVnumComB[j];
3349  jxE += pVnumComE[j];
3350  continue;
3351  }
3352 
3353  bId_np_j = bId * np + j;
3354  eId_np_j = eId * np + j;
3355  uId_np_j = uId * np + j;
3356  dP = bk.Pj[bId_np_j] - bk.Pj[eId_np_j] -
3357  conn.upblock_Rho[c * np + j] * dGamma;
3358  xi = bk.xi[uId_np_j];
3359  kr = bk.kr[uId_np_j];
3360  mu = bk.mu[uId_np_j];
3361  muP = bk.muP[uId_np_j];
3362  xiP = bk.xiP[uId_np_j];
3363  rhoP = bk.rhoP[uId_np_j];

3365

3367  xij = bk.xij[uId_np_j * nc + i];
3368  transIJ = xij * xi * transJ;

3371  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] += transIJ;
3372  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] -= transIJ;
3373 
3374  tmp = xij * transJ * xiP * dP;
3375  tmp += -transIJ * muP / mu * dP;
3376  if (!phaseExistE[j]) {
3377  tmp += transIJ * (-rhoP * dGamma);
3378  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] += tmp;
3379  } else if (!phaseExistB[j]) {
3380  tmp += transIJ * (-rhoP * dGamma);
3381  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] += tmp;
3382  } else {
3383  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] +=
3384  transIJ * (-bk.rhoP[bId_np_j] * dGamma) / 2;
3385  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] +=
3386  transIJ * (-bk.rhoP[eId_np_j] * dGamma) / 2;
3387  if (bId == uId) {
3388  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] += tmp;
3389  } else {
3390  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] += tmp;
3391  }
3392  }
3393 
3394  // Second var
3395  USI j1SB = 0;
3396  USI j1SE = 0;
3397  if (bId == uId) {
3398  // Saturation
3399  for (USI j1 = 0; j1 < np; j1++) {
3400  if (phasedS_B[j1]) {
3401  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + j1SB] +=
3402  transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[bId_np_j * np + j1];
3403  tmp = Akd * xij * xi / mu *
3404  bk.dKr_dS[uId_np_j * np + j1] * dP;
3405  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + j1SB] += tmp;
3406  j1SB++;
3407  }
3408  if (phasedS_E[j1]) {
3409  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + j1SE] -=
3410  transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[eId_np_j * np + j1];
3411  j1SE++;
3412  }
3413  }
3414  // Cij

3417  rhox = bk.rhox[uId_np_j * nc + k];
3418  xix = bk.xix[uId_np_j * nc + k];
3419  mux = bk.mux[uId_np_j * nc + k];

3421  tmp += xij * transJ * xix * dP;
3422  tmp += -transIJ * mux / mu * dP;
3423  tmp -= transIJ * dP / bk.nj[uId_np_j];
3424  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + k] += tmp;
3425  }
3426  // WARNING !!!
3427  if (i < pVnumComB[j])
3428  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + i] +=
3429  xi * transJ * dP / bk.nj[uId_np_j];
3430  } else {
3431  for (USI k = 0; k < pVnumComB[j]; k++) {
3432  rhox = bk.rhox[bId_np_j * nc + k] / 2;
3433  xix = bk.xix[uId_np_j * nc + k];
3434  mux = bk.mux[uId_np_j * nc + k];
3435  tmp = -transIJ * rhox * dGamma;
3436  tmp += xij * transJ * xix * dP;
3437  tmp += -transIJ * mux / mu * dP;
3438  tmp -= transIJ * dP / bk.nj[uId_np_j];
3439  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + k] += tmp;
3440  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + jxE + k] +=
3441  -transIJ * bk.rhox[eId_np_j * nc + k] / 2 * dGamma;
3442  }
3443  // WARNING !!!
3444  if (i < pVnumComB[j])
3445  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + i] +=
3446  xi * transJ * dP / bk.nj[uId_np_j];
3447  }
3448  } else {
3449  // Saturation
3450  for (USI j1 = 0; j1 < np; j1++) {
3451  if (phasedS_B[j1]) {
3452  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + j1SB] +=
3453  transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[bId_np_j * np + j1];
3454  j1SB++;
3455  }
3456  if (phasedS_E[j1]) {
3457  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + j1SE] -=
3458  transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[eId_np_j * np + j1];
3459  tmp = Akd * xij * xi / mu *
3460  bk.dKr_dS[uId_np_j * np + j1] * dP;
3461  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + j1SE] += tmp;
3462  j1SE++;
3463  }
3464  }
3465  // Cij
3466  if (!phaseExistB[j]) {
3467  for (USI k = 0; k < pVnumComE[j]; k++) {
3468  rhox = bk.rhox[uId_np_j * nc + k];
3469  xix = bk.xix[uId_np_j * nc + k];
3470  mux = bk.mux[uId_np_j * nc + k];
3471  tmp = -transIJ * rhox * dGamma;
3472  tmp += xij * transJ * xix * dP;
3473  tmp += -transIJ * mux / mu * dP;
3474  tmp -= transIJ * dP / bk.nj[uId_np_j];
3475  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + jxE + k] += tmp;
3476  }
3477  // WARNING !!!
3478  if (i < pVnumComE[j])
3479  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + jxE + i] +=
3480  xi * transJ * dP / bk.nj[uId_np_j];
3481  } else {
3482  for (USI k = 0; k < pVnumComE[j]; k++) {
3483  rhox = bk.rhox[eId_np_j * nc + k] / 2;

3486  tmp = -transIJ * rhox * dGamma;

3498  }
3499  }
3500  }
3501  jxB += pVnumComB[j];
3502  jxE += pVnumComE[j];
3503  }

3506  // Begin
3507  if (npB > 2) {
3508  fill(tmpb.begin(), tmpb.end(), 0.0);
3509  DaAxpby(ncol, ncolB, -1.0, dFdXsB.data(), &bk.res_n[bId * ncol2], 1.0,
3510  &tmpb[0]);

3523  ls.NewOffDiag(eId, bId, bmat);
3524

3528  }
3529 #endif
3530

3532  // End
3533  if (npE > 2) {

3535  DaAxpby(ncol, ncolE, -1.0, dFdXsE.data(), &bk.res_n[eId * ncol2], 1.0,

3580 void IsoT_FIMn::AssembleMatInjWellsNew(LinearSystem& ls, const Bulk& bk, const Well& wl, const OCP_DBL& dt) const

3583  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
3584  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
3585  const USI lendSdP = bk.maxLendSdP;
3586  const USI ncol = nc + 1;

3590  OCP_USI n_np_j;
3591

3597  vector<OCP_DBL> dQdXpW(bsize, 0);
3598  vector<OCP_DBL> dQdXsB(bsize2, 0);
3599  vector<char> phaseExistB(np, OCP_FALSE);
3600  vector<USI> pVnumComB(np, 0);
3601  vector<char> phasedS_B(np, OCP_FALSE);
3602  USI ncolB;
3603 
3604  OCP_DBL mu, muP, dP, transIJ;
3605 
3606  const OCP_USI wId = ls.AddDim(1) - 1;
3607  ls.NewDiag(wId, bmat);
3608 
3609  for (USI p = 0; p < wl.PerfNum(); p++) {
3610  const OCP_USI n = wl.PerfLocation(p);
3611  fill(dQdXpB.begin(), dQdXpB.end(), 0.0);
3612  fill(dQdXpW.begin(), dQdXpW.end(), 0.0);
3613  fill(dQdXsB.begin(), dQdXsB.end(), 0.0);
3614 
3615  dP = bk.P[n] - wl.BHP() - wl.DG(p);
3616 
3617  const USI npB = bk.phaseNum[n];
3618  USI jxB = 0;
3619  ncolB = 0;
3620  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
3621  phaseExistB[j] = bk.phaseExist[n * np + j];
3622  phasedS_B[j] = bk.pSderExist[n * np + j];
3623  if (phasedS_B[j]) jxB++;
3624  pVnumComB[j] = bk.pVnumCom[n * np + j];
3625  ncolB += pVnumComB[j];
3626  }
3627  ncolB += jxB;
3628 
3629  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
3630 
3631  if (!phaseExistB[j]) {
3632  jxB += pVnumComB[j];
3633  continue;
3634  }
3635 
3636  n_np_j = n * np + j;
3637  mu = bk.mu[n_np_j];
3638  muP = bk.muP[n_np_j];
3639 
3640  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
3641  // dQ / dP
3642  transIJ = wl.PerfTransj(p, j) * wl.PerfXi(p) * wl.InjZi(i);
3643  dQdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] += transIJ * (1 - dP * muP / mu);
3644  dQdXpW[(i + 1) * ncol] += -transIJ;
3645

3647  USI j1B = 0;
3648  for (USI j1 = 0; j1 < np; j1++) {
3649  if (phasedS_B[j1]) {
3650  dQdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + j1B] +=
3651  CONV1 * wl.PerfWI(p) * wl.PerfMultiplier(p) * wl.PerfXi(p) *
3652  wl.InjZi(i) * bk.dKr_dS[n_np_j * np + j1] * dP /
3653  mu;
3654  j1B++;
3655  }
3656  }
3657

3659  for (USI k = 0; k < pVnumComB[j]; k++) {
3660  dQdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + k] +=
3661  -transIJ * dP / mu * bk.mux[n_np_j * nc + k];
3662  }
3663  }
3664  jxB += pVnumComB[j];
3665  }
3666 
3667  // Assemble rhs
3668  // Well
3669  if (npB > 2) {
3670  fill(tmpb.begin(), tmpb.end(), 0.0);
3671  DaAxpby(ncol, ncolB, -1.0, dQdXsB.data(), &bk.res_n[n * ncol2], 1.0,
3672  &tmpb[0]);
3673  ls.AddRhs(n, tmpb);
3674  }

3677  bmat = dQdXpB;
3678  DaABpbC(ncol, ncol, ncolB, 1, dQdXsB.data(), &bk.dSec_dPri[n * lendSdP], 1,
3679  bmat.data());
3680  Dscalar(bsize, dt, bmat.data());
3681  // Bulk - Bulk -- add
3682  ls.AddDiag(n, bmat);
3683  // Bulk - Well -- insert
3684  bmat = dQdXpW;
3685  Dscalar(bsize, dt, bmat.data());
3686  ls.NewOffDiag(n, wId, bmat);
3687 
3688  // Well
3689  switch (wl.OptMode()) {
3690  case RATE_MODE:
3691  case ORATE_MODE:
3692  case GRATE_MODE:
3693  case WRATE_MODE:
3694  case LRATE_MODE:
3695  // Well - Well -- add
3696  fill(bmat.begin(), bmat.end(), 0.0);
3697  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
3698  bmat[0] += dQdXpW[(i + 1) * ncol];
3699  bmat[(i + 1) * ncol + i + 1] = 1;
3700  }
3701  ls.AddDiag(wId, bmat);
3702 
3703  // Well - Bulk -- insert
3704  bmat = dQdXpB;
3705  DaABpbC(ncol, ncol, ncolB, 1, dQdXsB.data(),
3706  &bk.dSec_dPri[n * lendSdP], 1, bmat.data());
3707  fill(bmat2.begin(), bmat2.end(), 0.0);
3708  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
3709  Daxpy(ncol, 1.0, bmat.data() + (i + 1) * ncol, bmat2.data());
3710  }
3711  ls.NewOffDiag(wId, n, bmat2);
3712  break;
3713 
3714  case BHP_MODE:
3715  // Well - Well -- add
3716  fill(bmat.begin(), bmat.end(), 0.0);
3717  for (USI i = 0; i < ncol; i++) {
3718  bmat[i * ncol + i] = 1;
3719  }
3720  ls.AddDiag(wId, bmat);
3721 
3722  // Well - Bulk -- insert
3723  fill(bmat.begin(), bmat.end(), 0.0);
3724  ls.NewOffDiag(wId, n, bmat);
3725  break;
3726 
3727  default:
3728  OCP_ABORT("Wrong Well Opt mode!");
3729  break;
3730  }
3731  }

3735 void IsoT_FIMn::AssembleMatProdWellsNew(LinearSystem& ls,
3736  const Bulk& bk,
3737  const Well& wl,
3738  const OCP_DBL& dt) const
3739 {
3740  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
3741  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
3742  const USI lendSdP = bk.maxLendSdP;
3743  const USI ncol = nc + 1;
3744  const USI ncol2 = np * nc + np;
3745  const USI bsize = ncol * ncol;
3746  const USI bsize2 = ncol * ncol2;
3747  OCP_USI n_np_j;
3748 
3749  vector<OCP_DBL> tmpb(ncol, 0);
3750  vector<OCP_DBL> bmat(bsize, 0);
3751  vector<OCP_DBL> bmat2(bsize, 0);
3752  vector<OCP_DBL> dQdXpB(bsize, 0);
3753  vector<OCP_DBL> dQdXpW(bsize, 0);
3754  vector<OCP_DBL> dQdXsB(bsize2, 0);
3755  vector<char> phaseExistB(np, OCP_FALSE);
3756  vector<char> phasedS_B(np, OCP_FALSE);
3757  vector<USI> pVnumComB(np, 0);
3758  USI ncolB;
3759 
3760  OCP_DBL xij, xi, mu, muP, xiP, dP, transIJ, tmp;
3761 
3762  const OCP_USI wId = ls.AddDim(1) - 1;
3763  ls.NewDiag(wId, bmat);
3764 
3765  // Set Prod Weight
3766  if (wl.OptMode() != BHP_MODE) wl.CalProdWeight(bk);
3767 
3768  for (USI p = 0; p < wl.PerfNum(); p++) {
3769  OCP_USI n = wl.PerfLocation(p);
3770  fill(dQdXpB.begin(), dQdXpB.end(), 0.0);
3771  fill(dQdXpW.begin(), dQdXpW.end(), 0.0);
3772  fill(dQdXsB.begin(), dQdXsB.end(), 0.0);
3773 
3774  const USI npB = bk.phaseNum[n];
3775  USI jxB = 0;
3776  ncolB = 0;
3777  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
3778  phaseExistB[j] = bk.phaseExist[n * np + j];
3779  phasedS_B[j] = bk.pSderExist[n * np + j];
3780  if (phasedS_B[j]) jxB++;
3781  pVnumComB[j] = bk.pVnumCom[n * np + j];
3782  ncolB += pVnumComB[j];
3783  }
3784  ncolB += jxB;
3785 
3786  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
3787 
3788  if (!phaseExistB[j]) {
3789  jxB += pVnumComB[j];
3790  continue;
3791  }
3792 
3793  n_np_j = n * np + j;
3794  dP = bk.Pj[n_np_j] - wl.BHP() - wl.DG(p);
3795  xi = bk.xi[n_np_j];
3796  mu = bk.mu[n_np_j];
3797  muP = bk.muP[n_np_j];
3798  xiP = bk.xiP[n_np_j];
3799 
3800  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
3801  xij = bk.xij[n_np_j * nc + i];
3802  // dQ / dP
3803  transIJ = wl.PerfTransj(p, j) * xi * xij;
3804  dQdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] +=
3805  transIJ * (1 - dP * muP / mu) + dP * wl.PerfTransj(p, j) * xij * xiP;
3806  dQdXpW[(i + 1) * ncol] += -transIJ;
3807 
3808  // dQ / dS
3809  USI j1B = 0;
3810  for (USI j1 = 0; j1 < np; j1++) {
3811  if (phasedS_B[j1]) {
3812  tmp = CONV1 * wl.PerfWI(p) * wl.PerfMultiplier(p) * dP / mu * xi *
3813  xij * bk.dKr_dS[n_np_j * np + j1];
3814  // capillary pressure
3815  tmp += transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[n_np_j * np + j1];
3816  dQdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + j1B] += tmp;
3817  j1B++;
3818  }
3819  }
3820 
3821  for (USI k = 0; k < pVnumComB[j]; k++) {
3822  tmp = dP * wl.PerfTransj(p, j) * xij *
3823  (bk.xix[n_np_j * nc + k] -
3824  xi / mu * bk.mux[n_np_j * nc + k]);
3825  tmp -= transIJ * dP / bk.nj[n_np_j];
3826  dQdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + k] += tmp;
3827  }
3828  // WARNING !!!
3829  if (i < pVnumComB[j])
3830  dQdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + i] +=
3831  wl.PerfTransj(p, j) * xi * dP / bk.nj[n_np_j];
3832  }
3833  jxB += pVnumComB[j];
3834  }
3835 
3836  // Assemble rhs
3837  // Well
3838  if (npB > 2) {
3839  fill(tmpb.begin(), tmpb.end(), 0.0);
3840  DaAxpby(ncol, ncolB, -1.0, dQdXsB.data(), &bk.res_n[n * ncol2], 1.0,
3841  &tmpb[0]);
3842  ls.AddRhs(n, tmpb);
3843  }
3844 
3845  // Bulk - Bulk -- add
3846  bmat = dQdXpB;
3847  DaABpbC(ncol, ncol, ncolB, 1, dQdXsB.data(), &bk.dSec_dPri[n * lendSdP], 1,
3848  bmat.data());
3849  Dscalar(bsize, dt, bmat.data());
3850  ls.AddDiag(n, bmat);
3851  // Bulk - Well -- insert
3852  bmat = dQdXpW;
3853  Dscalar(bsize, dt, bmat.data());
3854  ls.NewOffDiag(n, wId, bmat);
3855 
3856  // Well
3857  switch (wl.OptMode()) {
3858  case RATE_MODE:
3859  case ORATE_MODE:
3860  case GRATE_MODE:
3861  case WRATE_MODE:
3862  case LRATE_MODE:
3863  // Well - Well -- add
3864  fill(bmat.begin(), bmat.end(), 0.0);
3865  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
3866  bmat[0] += dQdXpW[(i + 1) * ncol] * wl.ProdWeight(i);
3867  bmat[(i + 1) * ncol + i + 1] = 1;
3868  }
3869  ls.AddDiag(wId, bmat);
3870 
3871  // Well - Bulk -- insert
3872  bmat = dQdXpB;
3873  DaABpbC(ncol, ncol, ncolB, 1, dQdXsB.data(),
3874  &bk.dSec_dPri[n * lendSdP], 1, bmat.data());
3875  fill(bmat2.begin(), bmat2.end(), 0.0);
3876  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
3877  Daxpy(ncol, wl.ProdWeight(i), bmat.data() + (i + 1) * ncol,
3878  bmat2.data());
3879  }
3880  ls.NewOffDiag(wId, n, bmat2);
3881  break;
3882 
3883  case BHP_MODE:
3884  // Well - Well -- add
3885  fill(bmat.begin(), bmat.end(), 0.0);
3886  for (USI i = 0; i < ncol; i++) {
3887  bmat[i * ncol + i] = 1;
3888  }
3889  ls.AddDiag(wId, bmat);
3890 
3891  // Well - Bulk -- insert
3892  fill(bmat.begin(), bmat.end(), 0.0);
3893  ls.NewOffDiag(wId, n, bmat);
3894  break;
3895 
3896  default:
3897  OCP_ABORT("Wrong Well Opt mode!");
3898  break;
3899  }
3900  }
3901 }

3905 void IsoT_FIMn::GetSolution(Reservoir& rs, const vector<OCP_DBL>& u, const OCPControl& ctrl) const
3906 {
3907  // For saturations changes:
3908  // 1. maximum changes must be less than dSmaxlim,
3909  // 2. if phases become mobile/immobile, then set it to crtical point,
3910  // 3. After saturations are determined, then scale the nij to conserve Volume
3911  // equations.
3912 
3913  // Bulk
3914  const OCP_DBL dSmaxlim = ctrl.ctrlNR.NRdSmax;
3915  // const OCP_DBL dPmaxlim = ctrl.ctrlNR.NRdPmax;
3916 
3917  Bulk& bk = rs.bulk;
3918  const OCP_USI nb = bk.numBulk;
3919  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
3920  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
3921  const USI row = np * (nc + 1);
3922  const USI col = nc + 1;
3923  vector<OCP_DBL> dtmp(row, 0);
3924  vector<OCP_DBL> tmpNij(np * nc, 0);
3925  OCP_USI n_np_j;
3926 
3927  bk.dSNR = bk.S;
3928  bk.NRphaseNum = bk.phaseNum;
3929  bk.NRdPmax = 0;
3930  bk.NRdNmax = 0;
3931 
3932 
3933  OCP_DBL dSmax;
3934  OCP_DBL dP;
3935  OCP_DBL chop = 1;
3936 
3937 
3938  for (OCP_USI n = 0; n < nb; n++) {
3939  const vector<OCP_DBL>& scm = bk.satcm[bk.SATNUM[n]];
3940 
3941  dP = u[n * col];
3942  bk.dPNR[n] = dP;
3943  bk.P[n] += dP; // seems better
3944  if (fabs(bk.NRdPmax) < fabs(dP)) bk.NRdPmax = dP;
3945 
3946  // rockVp[n] = rockVntg[n] * (1 + rockC1 * (P[n] - rockPref));
3947  // cout << scientific << setprecision(6) << dP << " " << n << endl;
3948 
3949  dSmax = 0;
3950  chop = 1;
3951 
3952  const USI cNp = bk.phaseNum[n];
3953  const USI len = bk.bRowSizedSdP[n];
3954  Dcopy(len, &dtmp[0], &bk.res_n[n * row]);
3955  DaAxpby(len, col, 1.0, &bk.dSec_dPri[n * bk.maxLendSdP], u.data() + n * col, 1.0,
3956  dtmp.data());
3957 
3958  // Calculate dSmax
3959  USI js = 0;
3960  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
3961  n_np_j = n * np + j;
3962  if (bk.pSderExist[n_np_j]) {
3963  dSmax = max(fabs(dtmp[js]), dSmax);
3964  js++;
3965  }
3966  }
3967 
3968  // Calculate chop
3969  if (dSmax > dSmaxlim) {
3970  chop = min(chop, dSmaxlim / dSmax);
3971  dSmax = dSmaxlim;
3972  }
3973  js = 0;
3974  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
3975  n_np_j = n * np + j;
3976  if (bk.pSderExist[n_np_j]) {
3977  if (fabs(bk.S[n_np_j] - scm[j]) > TINY &&
3978  (bk.S[n_np_j] - scm[j]) / (chop * dtmp[js]) < 0)
3979  chop *= min(1.0, -((bk.S[n_np_j] - scm[j]) / (chop * dtmp[js])));
3980  if (bk.S[n_np_j] + chop * dtmp[js] < 0)
3981  chop *= min(1.0, -bk.S[n_np_j] / (chop * dtmp[js]));
3982  js++;
3983  }
3984  }
3985 
3986  // Calculate S, phaseExist, xij, nj
3987  fill(tmpNij.begin(), tmpNij.end(), 0.0);
3988  // fill(Ni.begin() + n * nc, Ni.begin() + n * nc + nc, 0.0);
3989 
3990  js = 0;
3991  USI jx = cNp;
3992  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
3993  n_np_j = n * np + j;
3994  if (bk.pSderExist[n_np_j]) {
3995  bk.dSNRP[n_np_j] = chop * dtmp[js];
3996  js++;
3997 
3998  // S[n_np_j] += chop * dtmp[js];
3999  // if (S[n_np_j] < TINY) {
4000  // pSderExist[n_np_j] = OCP_FALSE;
4001  // }
4002  // js++;
4003  Daxpy(nc, bk.nj[n_np_j], &bk.xij[n_np_j * nc], &tmpNij[j * nc]);
4004  for (USI i = 0; i < bk.pVnumCom[j]; i++) {
4005  tmpNij[j * nc + i] += chop * dtmp[jx + i];
4006  }
4007  jx += bk.pVnumCom[j];
4008  bk.nj[n_np_j] = Dnorm1(nc, &tmpNij[j * nc]);
4009  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
4010  bk.xij[n_np_j * nc + i] = tmpNij[j * nc + i] / bk.nj[n_np_j];
4011  // Ni[n * nc + i] += tmpNij[j * nc + i];
4012  }
4013  }
4014  }
4015 
4016  // Vf correction
4017  /* OCP_DBL dVmin = 100 * rockVp[n];
4018  USI index = 0;
4019  for (USI j = 0; j < numPhase; j++) {
4020  if (phaseExist[n * numPhase + j]) {
4021  tmpxi[j] = flashCal[PVTNUM[n]]->XiPhase(P[n], T, &xij[(n *
4022  numPhase + j) * nc]); tmpVf[j] = nj[n * numPhase + j] / (S[n * numPhase +
4023  j] * tmpxi[j]); if (fabs(tmpVf[j] - rockVp[n]) < dVmin) { dVmin =
4024  fabs(tmpVf[j] - rockVp[n]); index = j;
4025  }
4026  }
4027  } */
4028  // for (USI j = 0; j < numPhase; j++) {
4029  // if (phaseExist[n * numPhase + j]) {
4030  // nj[n * numPhase + j] *= (tmpVf[index] / tmpVf[j]);
4031  // for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
4032  // Ni[n * nc + i] += nj[n * numPhase + j] * xij[(n * numPhase +
4033  // j) * nc + i];
4034  // }
4035  // }
4036  // }
4037 
4038  bk.NRstep[n] = chop;
4039  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
4040  bk.dNNR[n * nc + i] = u[n * col + 1 + i] * chop;
4041  if (fabs(bk.NRdNmax) < fabs(bk.dNNR[n * nc + i]) / bk.Nt[n])
4042  bk.NRdNmax = bk.dNNR[n * nc + i] / bk.Nt[n];
4043  bk.Ni[n * nc + i] += bk.dNNR[n * nc + i];
4044  }
4045  }
4046 
4047 
4048  // Well
4049  OCP_USI wId = nb * col;
4050  for (auto& wl : rs.allWells.wells) {
4051  if (wl.IsOpen()) {
4052  wl.SetBHP(wl.BHP() + u[wId]);
4053  wId += col;
4054  }
4055  }

4229 void IsoT_AIMc::FinishStep(Reservoir& rs, OCPControl& ctrl) const
