4453 
4454 void IsoT_AIMc::AssembleMatBulks(LinearSystem& ls,
4455  const Reservoir& rs,
4456  const OCP_DBL& dt) const
4457 {
4458  const Bulk& bk = rs.bulk;
4459  const BulkConn& conn = rs.conn;
4460  const OCP_USI nb = bk.numBulk;
4461  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
4462  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
4463  const USI ncol = nc + 1;
4464  const USI ncol2 = np * nc + np;
4465  const USI bsize = ncol * ncol;
4466  const USI bsize2 = ncol * ncol2;
4467  const USI lendSdP = bk.maxLendSdP;
4468 
4469  ls.AddDim(nb);
4470 
4471  vector<OCP_DBL> bmat(bsize, 0);
4472  // Accumulation term
4473  for (USI i = 1; i < nc + 1; i++) {
4474  bmat[i * ncol + i] = 1;
4475  }
4476  for (OCP_USI n = 0; n < nb; n++) {
4477  bmat[0] = bk.v[n] * bk.poroP[n] - bk.vfP[n];
4478  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
4479  bmat[i + 1] = -bk.vfi[n * nc + i];
4480  }
4481  ls.NewDiag(n, bmat);
4482  }
4483 
4484  // flux term
4485  OCP_DBL Akd;
4486  OCP_DBL transJ, transIJ;
4487  vector<OCP_DBL> dFdXpB(bsize, 0);
4488  vector<OCP_DBL> dFdXpE(bsize, 0);
4489  vector<OCP_DBL> dFdXsB(bsize2, 0);
4490  vector<OCP_DBL> dFdXsE(bsize2, 0);
4491  OCP_DBL* dFdXpI;
4492  OCP_DBL* dFdXsI;
4493  vector<OCP_BOOL> phaseExistB(np, OCP_FALSE);
4494  vector<OCP_BOOL> phaseExistE(np, OCP_FALSE);
4495  vector<OCP_BOOL> phaseExistI(np, OCP_FALSE);
4496  OCP_BOOL phaseExistU;
4497  vector<OCP_BOOL> phasedS_B(np, OCP_FALSE);
4498  vector<OCP_BOOL> phasedS_E(np, OCP_FALSE);
4499  vector<OCP_BOOL> phasedS_I(np, OCP_FALSE);
4500  vector<USI> pVnumComB(np, 0);
4501  vector<USI> pVnumComE(np, 0);
4502  vector<USI> pVnumComI(np, 0);
4503  OCP_USI ncolB, ncolE, ncolI;
4504 
4505  OCP_USI bId, eId, uId;
4506  OCP_USI bId_np_j, eId_np_j, uId_np_j, ibId_np_j;
4507  OCP_DBL kr, mu, xi, xij, rhoP, xiP, muP, rhox, xix, mux;
4508  OCP_DBL dP, dGamma;
4509  OCP_DBL tmp;
4510  OCP_BOOL bIdFIM, eIdFIM, uIdFIM;
4511 
4512  for (OCP_USI c = 0; c < conn.numConn; c++) {
4513  bId = conn.iteratorConn[c].BId();
4514  eId = conn.iteratorConn[c].EId();
4515  Akd = CONV1 * CONV2 * conn.iteratorConn[c].Area();
4516  dGamma = GRAVITY_FACTOR * (bk.depth[bId] - bk.depth[eId]);
4517  bIdFIM = eIdFIM = OCP_FALSE;
4518  if (bk.bulkTypeAIM.IfFIMbulk(bId)) bIdFIM = OCP_TRUE;
4519  if (bk.bulkTypeAIM.IfFIMbulk(eId)) eIdFIM = OCP_TRUE;
4520 
4521  if (!bIdFIM && !eIdFIM) {
4522  // both are explicit
4523  fill(dFdXpB.begin(), dFdXpB.end(), 0.0);
4524  fill(dFdXpE.begin(), dFdXpE.end(), 0.0);
4525  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
4526  phaseExistB[j] = bk.phaseExist[bId * np + j];
4527  phaseExistE[j] = bk.phaseExist[eId * np + j];
4528  uId = conn.upblock[c * np + j];
4529  phaseExistU = (uId == bId ? phaseExistB[j] : phaseExistE[j]);
4530  if (!phaseExistU) {
4531  continue;
4532  }
4533  bId_np_j = bId * np + j;
4534  eId_np_j = eId * np + j;
4535  uId_np_j = uId * np + j;
4536  xi = bk.xi[uId_np_j];
4537  kr = bk.kr[uId_np_j];
4538  mu = bk.mu[uId_np_j];
4539  transJ = Akd * xi * kr / mu;
4540  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
4541  xij = bk.xij[uId_np_j * nc + i];
4542  transIJ = xij * transJ;
4543  // Pressure -- Primary var
4544  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] += transIJ;
4545  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] -= transIJ;
4546  }
4547  }
4548  } else if ((bIdFIM && !eIdFIM) || (!bIdFIM && eIdFIM)) {
4549 
4550  // one is explicit, one is implicit
4551  fill(dFdXpB.begin(), dFdXpB.end(), 0.0);
4552  fill(dFdXpE.begin(), dFdXpE.end(), 0.0);
4553  fill(dFdXsB.begin(), dFdXsB.end(), 0.0);
4554  fill(dFdXsE.begin(), dFdXsE.end(), 0.0);
4555 
4556  ncolI = 0;
4557  USI jxI = 0;
4558  if (bIdFIM) {
4559  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
4560  phaseExistI[j] = bk.phaseExist[bId * np + j];
4561  phasedS_I[j] = bk.pSderExist[bId * np + j];
4562  if (phasedS_I[j]) jxI++;
4563  pVnumComI[j] = bk.pVnumCom[bId * np + j];
4564  ncolI += pVnumComI[j];
4565  }
4566  dFdXpI = &dFdXpB[0];
4567  dFdXsI = &dFdXsB[0];
4568  } else {
4569  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
4570  phaseExistI[j] = bk.phaseExist[eId * np + j];
4571  phasedS_I[j] = bk.pSderExist[eId * np + j];
4572  if (phasedS_I[j]) jxI++;
4573  pVnumComI[j] = bk.pVnumCom[eId * np + j];
4574  ncolI += pVnumComI[j];
4575  }
4576  dFdXpI = &dFdXpE[0];
4577  dFdXsI = &dFdXsE[0];
4578  }
4579  ncolI += jxI;
4580 
4581  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
4582  phaseExistB[j] = bk.phaseExist[bId * np + j];
4583  phaseExistE[j] = bk.phaseExist[eId * np + j];
4584  uId = conn.upblock[c * np + j];
4585  phaseExistU = (uId == bId ? phaseExistB[j] : phaseExistE[j]);
4586  if (!phaseExistU) {
4587  continue;
4588  }
4589 
4590  bId_np_j = bId * np + j;
4591  eId_np_j = eId * np + j;
4592  uId_np_j = uId * np + j;
4593  dP = bk.Pj[bId_np_j] - bk.Pj[eId_np_j] -
4594  conn.upblock_Rho[c * np + j] * dGamma;
4595  xi = bk.xi[uId_np_j];
4596  kr = bk.kr[uId_np_j];
4597  mu = bk.mu[uId_np_j];
4598  transJ = Akd * kr / mu;
4599  uIdFIM = (uId == bId ? bIdFIM : eIdFIM);
4600 
4601  if (bIdFIM)
4602  ibId_np_j = bId_np_j;
4603  else
4604  ibId_np_j = eId_np_j;
4605 
4606  if (uIdFIM) {
4607  // upblock is implicit
4608  OCP_DBL rhoWgt = 1.0;
4609  if (phaseExistB[j] && phaseExistE[j]) rhoWgt = 0.5;
4610 
4611  muP = bk.muP[ibId_np_j];
4612  xiP = bk.xiP[ibId_np_j];
4613  rhoP = bk.rhoP[ibId_np_j];
4614  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
4615  xij = bk.xij[ibId_np_j * nc + i];
4616  transIJ = xij * xi * transJ;
4617 
4618  // Pressure -- Primary var
4619  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] += transIJ;
4620  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] -= transIJ;
4621 
4622  tmp = transIJ * (-rhoP * dGamma) * rhoWgt;
4623  tmp += xij * transJ * xiP * dP;
4624  tmp += -transIJ * muP / mu * dP;
4625  dFdXpI[(i + 1) * ncol] += tmp;
4626 
4627  USI j1S = 0;
4628  // Saturation -- Second var
4629  for (USI j1 = 0; j1 < np; j1++) {
4630  if (phasedS_I[j1]) {
4631  dFdXsI[(i + 1) * ncolI + j1S] +=
4632  transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[ibId_np_j * np + j1];
4633  tmp = Akd * xij * xi / mu *
4634  bk.dKr_dS[ibId_np_j * np + j1] * dP;
4635  dFdXsI[(i + 1) * ncolI + j1S] += tmp;
4636  j1S++;
4637  }
4638  }
4639  // Cij
4640  for (USI k = 0; k < pVnumComI[j]; k++) {
4641  rhox = bk.rhox[ibId_np_j * nc + k] * rhoWgt;
4642  xix = bk.xix[ibId_np_j * nc + k];
4643  mux = bk.mux[ibId_np_j * nc + k];
4644  tmp = -transIJ * rhox * dGamma;
4645  tmp += xij * transJ * xix * dP;
4646  tmp += -transIJ * mux / mu * dP;
4647  dFdXsI[(i + 1) * ncolI + jxI + k] += tmp;
4648  }
4649  // WARNING !!!
4650  if (i < pVnumComI[j])
4651  dFdXsI[(i + 1) * ncolI + jxI + i] += xi * transJ * dP;
4652  }
4653  jxI += pVnumComI[j];
4654  } else {
4655  // downblock is implicit
4656  OCP_DBL rhoWgt = 0;
4657  if (phaseExistB[j] && phaseExistE[j]) rhoWgt = 0.5;
4658  rhoP = bk.rhoP[ibId_np_j];
4659 
4660  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
4661  xij = bk.xij[uId_np_j * nc + i];
4662  transIJ = xij * xi * transJ;
4663 
4664  // Pressure -- Primary var
4665  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] += transIJ;
4666  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] -= transIJ;
4667 
4668  tmp = transIJ * (-rhoP * dGamma) * rhoWgt;
4669  dFdXpI[(i + 1) * ncol] += tmp;
4670 
4671  USI j1S = 0;
4672  // Saturation -- Second var
4673  for (USI j1 = 0; j1 < np; j1++) {
4674  if (phasedS_I[j1]) {
4675  dFdXsI[(i + 1) * ncolI + j1S] +=
4676  transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[ibId_np_j * np + j1];
4677  j1S++;
4678  }
4679  }
4680  // Cij
4681  for (USI k = 0; k < pVnumComI[j]; k++) {
4682  rhox = bk.rhox[ibId_np_j * nc + k] * rhoWgt;
4683  tmp = -transIJ * rhox * dGamma;
4684  dFdXsI[(i + 1) * ncolI + jxI + k] += tmp;
4685  }
4686  }
4687  jxI += pVnumComI[j];
4688  }
4689  }
4690  } else {
4691  // both are implicit
4692  fill(dFdXpB.begin(), dFdXpB.end(), 0.0);
4693  fill(dFdXpE.begin(), dFdXpE.end(), 0.0);
4694  fill(dFdXsB.begin(), dFdXsB.end(), 0.0);
4695  fill(dFdXsE.begin(), dFdXsE.end(), 0.0);
4696 
4697  USI jxB = 0;
4698  USI jxE = 0;
4699  ncolB = 0;
4700  ncolE = 0;
4701 
4702  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
4703  phaseExistB[j] = bk.phaseExist[bId * np + j];
4704  phaseExistE[j] = bk.phaseExist[eId * np + j];
4705  phasedS_B[j] = bk.pSderExist[bId * np + j];
4706  phasedS_E[j] = bk.pSderExist[eId * np + j];
4707  if (phasedS_B[j]) jxB++;
4708  if (phasedS_E[j]) jxE++;
4709  pVnumComB[j] = bk.pVnumCom[bId * np + j];
4710  pVnumComE[j] = bk.pVnumCom[eId * np + j];
4711  ncolB += pVnumComB[j];
4712  ncolE += pVnumComE[j];
4713  }
4714  ncolB += jxB;
4715  ncolE += jxE;
4716 
4717  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
4718  uId = conn.upblock[c * np + j];
4719 
4720  phaseExistU = (uId == bId ? phaseExistB[j] : phaseExistE[j]);
4721  if (!phaseExistU) {
4722  jxB += pVnumComB[j];

4726

4728  eId_np_j = eId * np + j;
4729  uId_np_j = uId * np + j;
4730  dP = bk.Pj[bId_np_j] - bk.Pj[eId_np_j] -
4731  conn.upblock_Rho[c * np + j] * dGamma;
4732  xi = bk.xi[uId_np_j];
4733  kr = bk.kr[uId_np_j];
4734  mu = bk.mu[uId_np_j];
4735  muP = bk.muP[uId_np_j];
4736  xiP = bk.xiP[uId_np_j];
4737  rhoP = bk.rhoP[uId_np_j];
4738  transJ = Akd * kr / mu;
4739 
4740  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
4741  xij = bk.xij[uId_np_j * nc + i];
4742  transIJ = xij * xi * transJ;
4743 
4744  // Pressure -- Primary var
4745  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] += transIJ;
4746  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] -= transIJ;
4747 
4748  tmp = xij * transJ * xiP * dP;
4749  tmp += -transIJ * muP / mu * dP;
4750  if (!phaseExistE[j]) {
4751  tmp += transIJ * (-rhoP * dGamma);
4752  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] += tmp;
4753  } else if (!phaseExistB[j]) {
4754  tmp += transIJ * (-rhoP * dGamma);
4755  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] += tmp;
4756  } else {
4757  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] +=
4758  transIJ * (-bk.rhoP[bId_np_j] * dGamma) / 2;
4759  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] +=
4760  transIJ * (-bk.rhoP[eId_np_j] * dGamma) / 2;
4761  if (bId == uId) {
4762  dFdXpB[(i + 1) * ncol] += tmp;
4763  } else {
4764  dFdXpE[(i + 1) * ncol] += tmp;
4765  }
4766  }
4767 
4768  // Second var
4769  USI j1SB = 0;
4770  USI j1SE = 0;
4771  if (bId == uId) {
4772  // Saturation
4773  for (USI j1 = 0; j1 < np; j1++) {
4774  if (phasedS_B[j1]) {
4775  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + j1SB] +=
4776  transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[bId_np_j * np + j1];
4777  tmp = Akd * xij * xi / mu *
4778  bk.dKr_dS[uId_np_j * np + j1] * dP;
4779  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + j1SB] += tmp;
4780  j1SB++;
4781  }
4782  if (phasedS_E[j1]) {
4783  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + j1SE] -=
4784  transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[eId_np_j * np + j1];
4785  j1SE++;
4786  }
4787  }
4788  // Cij
4789  if (!phaseExistE[j]) {
4790  for (USI k = 0; k < pVnumComB[j]; k++) {
4791  rhox = bk.rhox[uId_np_j * nc + k];
4792  xix = bk.xix[uId_np_j * nc + k];
4793  mux = bk.mux[uId_np_j * nc + k];
4794  tmp = -transIJ * rhox * dGamma;
4795  tmp += xij * transJ * xix * dP;
4796  tmp += -transIJ * mux / mu * dP;
4797  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + k] += tmp;
4798  }
4799  // WARNING !!!
4800  if (i < pVnumComB[j])
4801  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + i] += xi * transJ * dP;
4802  } else {
4803  for (USI k = 0; k < pVnumComB[j]; k++) {
4804  rhox = bk.rhox[bId_np_j * nc + k] / 2;
4805  xix = bk.xix[uId_np_j * nc + k];
4806  mux = bk.mux[uId_np_j * nc + k];
4807  tmp = -transIJ * rhox * dGamma;
4808  tmp += xij * transJ * xix * dP;
4809  tmp += -transIJ * mux / mu * dP;
4810  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + k] += tmp;
4811  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + jxE + k] +=
4812  -transIJ * bk.rhox[eId_np_j * nc + k] / 2 *
4813  dGamma;
4814  }
4815  // WARNING !!!
4816  if (i < pVnumComB[j])
4817  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + i] += xi * transJ * dP;
4818  }
4819  } else {
4820  // Saturation
4821  for (USI j1 = 0; j1 < np; j1++) {
4822  if (phasedS_B[j1]) {
4823  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + j1SB] +=
4824  transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[bId_np_j * np + j1];
4825  j1SB++;
4826  }
4827  if (phasedS_E[j1]) {
4828  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + j1SE] -=
4829  transIJ * bk.dPcj_dS[eId_np_j * np + j1];
4830  tmp = Akd * xij * xi / mu *
4831  bk.dKr_dS[uId_np_j * np + j1] * dP;
4832  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + j1SE] += tmp;
4833  j1SE++;
4834  }
4835  }
4836  // Cij
4837  if (!phaseExistB[j]) {
4838  for (USI k = 0; k < pVnumComE[j]; k++) {
4839  rhox = bk.rhox[uId_np_j * nc + k];
4840  xix = bk.xix[uId_np_j * nc + k];
4841  mux = bk.mux[uId_np_j * nc + k];
4842  tmp = -transIJ * rhox * dGamma;
4843  tmp += xij * transJ * xix * dP;
4844  tmp += -transIJ * mux / mu * dP;
4845  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + jxE + k] += tmp;
4846  }
4847  // WARNING !!!
4848  if (i < pVnumComE[j])
4849  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + jxE + i] += xi * transJ * dP;
4850  } else {
4851  for (USI k = 0; k < pVnumComE[j]; k++) {
4852  rhox = bk.rhox[eId_np_j * nc + k] / 2;
4853  xix = bk.xix[uId_np_j * nc + k];
4854  mux = bk.mux[uId_np_j * nc + k];
4855  tmp = -transIJ * rhox * dGamma;
4856  tmp += xij * transJ * xix * dP;
4857  tmp += -transIJ * mux / mu * dP;
4858  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + jxE + k] += tmp;
4859  dFdXsB[(i + 1) * ncolB + jxB + k] +=
4860  -transIJ * bk.rhox[bId_np_j * nc + k] / 2 *
4861  dGamma;
4862  }
4863  // WARNING !!!
4864  if (i < pVnumComE[j])
4865  dFdXsE[(i + 1) * ncolE + jxE + i] += xi * transJ * dP;
4866  }
4867  }
4868  }
4869  jxB += pVnumComB[j];
4870  jxE += pVnumComE[j];
4871  }
4872  }
4873 
4874  if (bIdFIM && !eIdFIM)
4875  ncolB = ncolI;
4876  else if (!bIdFIM && eIdFIM)
4877  ncolE = ncolI;
4878 
4879  // Assemble
4880  bmat = dFdXpB;
4881  if (bIdFIM) {
4882  DaABpbC(ncol, ncol, ncolB, 1, dFdXsB.data(),
4883  &bk.dSec_dPri[bId * lendSdP], 1, bmat.data());
4884  }
4885  Dscalar(bsize, dt, bmat.data());
4886  // Begin - Begin -- add
4887  ls.AddDiag(bId, bmat);
4888  // End - Begin -- insert
4889  Dscalar(bsize, -1, bmat.data());
4890  ls.NewOffDiag(eId, bId, bmat);
4891 
4892 #ifdef OCP_NANCHECK
4893  if (!CheckNan(bmat.size(), &bmat[0])) {
4894  OCP_ABORT("INF or NAN in bmat !");
4895  }
4896 #endif
4897 
4898  // End
4899  bmat = dFdXpE;
4900  if (eIdFIM) {
4901  DaABpbC(ncol, ncol, ncolE, 1, dFdXsE.data(),
4902  &bk.dSec_dPri[eId * lendSdP], 1, bmat.data());
4903  }
4904  Dscalar(bsize, dt, bmat.data());
4905  // Begin - End -- insert
4906  ls.NewOffDiag(bId, eId, bmat);
4907  // End - End -- add
4908  Dscalar(bsize, -1, bmat.data());
4909  ls.AddDiag(eId, bmat);
4910 
4911 #ifdef OCP_NANCHECK
4912  if (!CheckNan(bmat.size(), &bmat[0])) {
4913  OCP_ABORT("INF or NAN in bmat !");
4914  }
4915 #endif
4916  }
4917 }

4920 void IsoT_AIMc::GetSolution(Reservoir& rs,
4921  const vector<OCP_DBL>& u,
4922  const OCPControl& ctrl) const
4923 {
4924  // Bulk
4925  const OCP_DBL dSmaxlim = ctrl.ctrlNR.NRdSmax;
4926  // const OCP_DBL dPmaxlim = ctrl.ctrlNR.NRdPmax;
4927 
4928  Bulk& bk = rs.bulk;
4929  const OCP_USI nb = bk.numBulk;
4930  const USI np = bk.numPhase;
4931  const USI nc = bk.numCom;
4932  const USI row = np * (nc + 1);
4933  const USI col = nc + 1;
4934  vector<OCP_DBL> dtmp(row, 0);
4935  OCP_DBL chopmin = 1;
4936  OCP_DBL choptmp = 0;
4937  OCP_USI n_np_j;
4938 
4939  bk.dSNR = bk.S;
4940  bk.NRphaseNum = bk.phaseNum;
4941  bk.NRdPmax = 0;
4942  bk.NRdNmax = 0;
4943 
4944 
4945  for (OCP_USI n = 0; n < nb; n++) {
4946  if (bk.bulkTypeAIM.IfIMPECbulk(n)) {
4947  // IMPEC Bulk
4948  // Pressure
4949  OCP_DBL dP = u[n * col];
4950  bk.NRdPmax = max(bk.NRdPmax, fabs(dP));
4951  bk.P[n] += dP; // seems better
4952  bk.dPNR[n] = dP;
4953  bk.NRstep[n] = 1;
4954  // Ni
4955  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
4956  bk.dNNR[n * nc + i] = u[n * col + 1 + i];
4957  bk.Ni[n * nc + i] += bk.dNNR[n * nc + i];
4958  }
4959  // Pj
4960  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
4961  bk.Pj[n * np + j] = bk.P[n] + bk.Pc[n * np + j];
4962  }
4963  continue;
4964  }
4965 
4966  chopmin = 1;
4967  // compute the chop
4968  fill(dtmp.begin(), dtmp.end(), 0.0);
4969  DaAxpby(bk.bRowSizedSdP[n], col, 1, &bk.dSec_dPri[n * bk.maxLendSdP], u.data() + n * col,
4970  1, dtmp.data());
4971 
4972  USI js = 0;
4973  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
4974  if (!bk.pSderExist[n * np + j]) {
4975  continue;
4976  }
4977  n_np_j = n * np + j;
4978 
4979  choptmp = 1;
4980  if (fabs(dtmp[js]) > dSmaxlim) {
4981  choptmp = dSmaxlim / fabs(dtmp[js]);
4982  } else if (bk.S[n_np_j] + dtmp[js] < 0.0) {
4983  choptmp = 0.9 * bk.S[n_np_j] / fabs(dtmp[js]);
4984  }
4985 
4986  // if (fabs(S[n_np_j] - scm[j]) > TINY &&
4987  // (S[n_np_j] - scm[j]) / (choptmp * dtmp[js]) < 0)
4988  // choptmp *= min(1.0, -((S[n_np_j] - scm[j]) / (choptmp * dtmp[js])));
4989 
4990  chopmin = min(chopmin, choptmp);
4991  js++;
4992  }
4993 
4994  // dS
4995  js = 0;
4996  for (USI j = 0; j < np; j++) {
4997  if (!bk.pSderExist[n * np + j]) {
4998  bk.dSNRP[n * np + j] = 0;
4999  continue;
5000  }
5001  bk.dSNRP[n * np + j] = chopmin * dtmp[js];
5002  js++;
5003  }
5004 
5005  // dxij ---- Compositional model only
5006  if (bk.IfUseEoS()) {
5007  if (bk.phaseNum[n] >= 3) {
5008  OCP_USI bId = 0;
5009  for (USI j = 0; j < 2; j++) {
5010  bId = n * np * nc + j * nc;
5011  for (USI i = 0; i < bk.numComH; i++) {
5012  bk.xij[bId + i] += chopmin * dtmp[js];
5013  js++;
5014  }
5015  }
5016  }
5017  }
5018 
5019  // dP
5020  OCP_DBL dP = u[n * col];
5021  if (fabs(bk.NRdPmax) < fabs(dP)) bk.NRdPmax = dP;
5022  bk.P[n] += dP; // seems better
5023  bk.dPNR[n] = dP;
5024 
5025  // dNi
5026  bk.NRstep[n] = chopmin;
5027  for (USI i = 0; i < nc; i++) {
5028  bk.dNNR[n * nc + i] = u[n * col + 1 + i] * chopmin;
5029  if (fabs(bk.NRdNmax) < fabs(bk.dNNR[n * nc + i]) / bk.Nt[n])
5030  bk.NRdNmax = bk.dNNR[n * nc + i] / bk.Nt[n];
5031 
5032  bk.Ni[n * nc + i] += bk.dNNR[n * nc + i];
5033  }
5034  }
5035 
5036  // Well
5037  OCP_USI wId = nb * col;
5038  for (auto& wl : rs.allWells.wells) {
5039  if (wl.IsOpen()) {
5040  wl.SetBHP(wl.BHP() + u[wId]);
5041  wId += col;
5042  }
5043  }
5044 }
